var book = {
	"name": "Asomafoɔ",
	"numChapters": 28,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Teofilo, akane nwoma a meyɛeɛ no fa nnoɔma a Yesu firii aseɛ yɛeɛ, na ɔkyerɛkyerɛeɛ nyinaa",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> de bɛsii da a ɔnam Honhom Kronkron soɔ maa asomafoɔ a ɔyii wɔn no ahyɛdeɛ, na wɔfaa no kɔɔ soro no ho.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Wɔn nso na n’amanehunu akyiri no, ɔnam adanseɛ bebree so yii ne ho kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ ɔteasefoɔ adaduanan mu maa wɔhunuu no, na ɔkaa Nyankopɔn ahennie ho asɛm.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔne wɔn hyiaeɛ no, ɔhyɛɛ wɔn sɛ wɔmmfiri Yerusalem nnkɔ, na mmom wɔntwɛn Agya no bɔhyɛ a ɔse: Mote firii m’anomu no,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> sɛ Yohane deɛ, ɔde nsuo na ɛbɔɔ asu, na mo deɛ, nna yi mu, ɛrenkyɛ na wɔbɛbɔ mo asu Honhom Kronkron mu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɛnna wɔhyiaeɛ no, wɔbisaa no sɛ: Awurade, berɛ yi mu na wobɛsane de ahennie no ama Israel anaa?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔbuaa wɔn sɛ: Ɛnyɛ mo asɛm, sɛ mobɛhunu berɛ anaa nna a Agya no ahyɛ ato hɔ ɔno ara ne tumi mu,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na mmom sɛ Honhom Kronkron no nya ba mo so a, mobɛnya ahoɔden, na moayɛ m’adansefoɔ Yerusalem ne Yudea nyinaa ne Samaria de akɔpem asase ano nohoa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔkaa yeinom wieeɛ na wɔrehwɛ no no, wɔmaa no so, na mununkum gyee no firii wɔn anim.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɔrekorɔ na wɔrehwɛ soro haa no, hwɛ, mmarima baanu bi a wɔhyɛ ntadeɛ fitaa bɛgyinaa wɔn nkyɛn,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na wɔkaa nso sɛ: Galilea mmarima, adɛn na mogyina ha rehwɛ soro yi? Yesu yi ara a wɔafa no mo nkyɛn kɔ soro yi, ɔbɛba saa ara, sɛdeɛ mohu no sɛ ɔrekɔ soro yi.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛno na wɔfirii bepɔ a wɔfrɛ no Ngo Bepɔ a ɛbɛn Yerusalem bɛyɛ homeda kwan no so sane kɔɔ Yerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na wɔduruu hɔ no, wɔkɔɔ abansoro dan no mu; ɛhɔ na na Petro ne Yohane ne Yakobo ne Andrea, Filipo ne Toma, Bartolomeo ne Mateo, Alfeo ba Yakobo ne Simon Selote ne Yakobo ba Yuda teɛ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na yeinom nyinaa de akoma korɔ kura mpaebɔ mu ara, wɔne mmaa no ne Maria, Yesu ne na ne ne nuanom.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na nna yi mu Petro sɔre gyinaa anuanom no mfimfini (na nkurɔfokuo a wɔahyia faako no bɛyɛ nnipa ɔha aduonu) na ɔkaa sɛ:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Anuanom, ɛtwa sɛ twerɛ no a Honhom Kronkron nam Dawid anomu nsɛm so kaa no akane no nya ba mu wɔ Yuda a ɔyɛɛ wɔn a wɔkyeree Yesu no kwankyerɛfoɔ no ho.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na wɔkann no fraa yɛn, na ɔnyaa ɛsom yi kyɛfa bi somee.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> (Saa Yuda yi na ɔde n’amumuyɛ akatua nyaa asase, na ne nkɔnkɔ bɛwɔɔ hɔ no, ne mu paee, na ne yam adeɛ nyinaa tu gui;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na wɔn a wɔte Yerusalem nyinaa tee, na wɔfrɛɛ asase no wɔn ara wɔn kasa mu sɛ Hakeldama, aseɛ ne Mogya Asase.)",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na wɔatwerɛ no Nnwom nwoma mu sɛ: Ne tenaberɛ nyɛ amamfo, na obiara nntena mu! Na ne hwɛ adwuma no deɛ, ɔfoforɔ mfa!",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Enti ɛtwa sɛ mmarima a wɔne yɛn nanteeɛ berɛ a Awurade Yesu dii yɛn mu ahyemfire no nyinaa",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> firi Yohane asubɔ so de bɛsi da a wɔfaa no yɛn nkyɛn kɔɔ soro no mu baako ne yɛn yɛ ne sɔreɛ ho adansefoɔ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wɔde baanu bɛgyinaa hɔ, Yosef a wɔfrɛ no Barsaba a wɔtoo no Yusto no, ne Matia.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na wɔbɔɔ mpaeɛ sɛ: Wo, Awurade a wonim nnipa nyinaa akoma mu, kyerɛ baanu yi mu baako a woayi no",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> sɛ ɔmfa ɛsom yi ne asomafodwuma a Yuda firii mu teree ho sɛ ɔrekɔ ɔno ara tenaberɛ no kyɛfa no nsom!",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na wɔtwee wɔn so ntonto; na ntonto no bɔɔ Matia, na wɔkann no kaa asomafoɔ dubaako no ho."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Pentekoste da no duruiɛ no, na wɔn nyinaa ahyia faako.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na mpofirim no, ahum bi a ɛte sɛ mframa a emu yɛ den a ɛrebɔ firi soro bae, na ɛbɛhyɛɛ efie a wɔte mu no ma.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na tɛkyerɛma a wɔapaepae mu a ɛte sɛ ogya yiyi kyerɛɛ wɔn, na ɛbɛsisii wɔn atifi mmaako mmaako.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Honhom Kronkron yɛɛ wɔn nyinaa mama, na wɔfirii aseɛ kasaa kasa foforɔ, sɛdeɛ Honhom no maa wɔn sɛ wɔnka.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Yudafoɔ bi a wɔyɛ nnipa nyamesurofoɔ a wɔfiri wiase aman nyinaa mu te Yerusalem.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na wɔtee deɛ ɛrekɔ so no, nnipa pii bɛhyiae, na wɔn adwene mu yɛɛ wɔn keserenee sɛ obiara tee sɛ wɔreka ne kurom kasa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɛyɛɛ wɔn nyinaa ahodwiri ne nwanwa, na wɔkaa sɛ: Hwɛ, wɔn a wɔrekasa yi nyinaa nyɛ Galileafoɔ anaa?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɛyɛɛ dɛn na yɛn nyinaa te yɛn ara yɛn kasa a wɔwoo yɛn mu yi?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Partifoɔ ne Mediafoɔ ne Elamfoɔ ne wɔn a wɔte Mesopotamia ne Yudea ne Kapadokia, Ponto ne Asia,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Frigia ne Pamfilia, Misraim ne Libia fa a ɛfa Kirene, ne ahɔhoɔ a wɔfiri Roma, Yudafoɔ ne wɔn a wɔadane Yudafoɔ,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kretafoɔ ne Arabfoɔ, yɛte sɛ wɔde yɛn kasa ka Nyankopɔn nnwuma akɛseɛ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɛyɛɛ wɔn nyinaa ahodwiri, na wɔn tirim yɛɛ wɔn keserenee, na wɔsesee wɔn ho sɛ: Yei ase ne sɛn?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ebinom nso de dii fɛw sɛ: Nsa foforɔ na abo wɔn.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Petro ne dubaako no sɔre gyinae, na ɔmaa ne nne so ka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Yuda mmarima ne mo a mote Yerusalem nyinaa, monhunu yei, na momma me nsɛm yi nkɔ mo aso mu!",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na yeinom mmoroo nsa, sɛdeɛ mosusuo yi, ɛfiri sɛ ɛyɛ anɔpa nnɔnkron.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na yei ne deɛ Odiyifoɔ Yoel kaeɛ no",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> sɛ Onyankopɔn se: Na ɛbɛba sɛ nna a ɛdi akyire no mu no, mɛhwie me Honhom no magu honam nyinaa so, na mo mmammarima ne mo mmammaa ahyɛ nkɔm, na mo mmeranteɛ ahunhunu anisoadeɛ, na mo mpanimfoɔ asoso daeɛ;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na me nkoa ne me mfenaa so na nna no mu mɛhwie me Honhom no bi maguo, na wɔahyɛ nkɔm.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na mɛma anwanwadeɛ aba ewiem wɔ ɔsoro, na nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ aba asase so ɛfam, mogya ne ogya ne wisie kumoo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Owia bɛdane sum, na ɔsrane adane mogya ansa na Awurade da kɛseɛ a ɛhyerɛn no aba.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɛbɛba sɛ obiara a ɔbɛbɔ Awurade din no, wɔbɛgye no nkwa.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Israel mmarima, montie nsɛm yi! Yesu, Nasareni no, ɔbarima a Onyankopɔn de ahoɔdenneɛ ne anwanwadeɛ ne nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ a ɔno Onyankopɔn no ara nam ne so yɛɛ no mo mu yii no kyerɛɛ mo, sɛdeɛ mo ara nso monim no,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ɔno ara a wɔnam Nyankopɔn agyina a ɔtuiɛ, ne ne nim a ɔnim dada so yii no maeɛ no, na mofaa no, nam wɔn a wɔnni mmara nsa soɔ bɔɔ no asɛnnua mu kumm no.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ɔno na Onyankopɔn anyane no, na wasane owuya homa, ɛfiri sɛ antumi amma sɛ ɛka no hyɛ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na Dawid kaa ne ho asɛm sɛ: Mehunuu Awurade m’anim daa, ɛfiri sɛ ɔwɔ me nifa na manhinhim.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Yei nti m’akoma tɔɔ me yam, na me tɛkyerɛma ho sanee no; na me honam nso bɛda anidasoɔ mu,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ɛfiri sɛ worennya me kra Asamando, na woremma wo Kronkronni no nhunu porɔeɛ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Wokyerɛɛ me nkwa akwan; wode w’anim bɛma abotɔyam amee me.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Anuanom, momma me kwan na menka agya panin Dawid ho asɛm pefee menkyerɛ mo, sɛ wawu, na wɔasie no, na ne da wɔ yɛn nkyɛn ha de bɛsi nnɛ.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na sɛ ɔyɛ odiyifoɔ, na ɔnim sɛ Onyankopɔn de ntam ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ n’asene mu aba mu bi na ɔbɛtena n’ahennwa soɔ nti,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> ɔhunuu yei siee, na ɔkaa Kristo sɔreɛ ho asɛm sɛ wɔannya no Asamando, nanso ne honam anhunu porɔeɛ.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Yesu yi ara na Onyankopɔn anyane no; ɛho adansefoɔ na yɛn nyinaa yɛ.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Afei wɔmaa no so kɔɔ Nyankopɔn nifa, na ɔnyaa Agya no nkyɛn Honhom Kronkron bɔhyɛ nti na wahwie deɛ mohunu na moteɛ yi aguo.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na Dawid ankɔ soro; nanso ɔno ara kaa sɛ: Awurade ka kyerɛɛ me wura sɛ: Tena me nifa",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> kɔsi sɛ mede w’atamfo bɛyɛ wo nan ase ntiasoɔ.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Enti ma Israel fie nyinaa nhunu ampa sɛ Onyankopɔn de Yesu yi ara a mosɛnee no no ayɛ Awurade ne Kristo.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na wɔteeɛ no, ɛwowɔɔ wɔn akoma mu, na wɔka kyerɛɛ Petro ne asomafoɔ a aka no sɛ: Anuanom, yɛnyɛ dɛn?",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Na Petro see wɔn sɛ: Monsakyera mo adwene, na mo nyinaa mma wɔmmɔ mo asu Yesu Kristo din mu, mma mo bɔne fakyɛ, na mobɛnya Honhom Kronkron akyɛdeɛ no.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na bɔhyɛ no yɛ mo ne mo mma ne wɔn a wɔwɔ akyirikyiri, a Awurade yɛn Nyankopɔn bɛfrɛ wɔn aba nyinaa dea.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na ɔde nsɛm bebree kaa ho dii wɔn adanseɛ, na ɔtuu wɔn fo sɛ: Momma wɔnnye mo mfiri nnɛ mma abusua kontonkye yi mu!",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ɛnna wɔn a wɔgyee n’asɛm no maa wɔbɔɔ wɔn asu. Na da no ara wɔde akra bɛyɛ mpensa bɛkaa wɔn ho.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na wɔkura asomafoɔ no nkyerɛkyerɛ ne ayɔnkofa ne paanoobubuo ne mpaebɔ mu ara.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Na ehu baa nnipa nyinaa so, na asomafoɔ no yɛɛ anwanwadeɛ ne nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ pii.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Na wɔn a wɔgye diiɛ nyinaa hyiaa faako, na wɔn nnoɔma nyinaa yɛ kwasafodeɛ,",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> na wɔtɔn wɔn ahonyadeɛ ne wɔn nnoɔma, na wɔkyɛɛ mu maa wɔn nyinaa, sɛdeɛ ɛhia obiara.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Na daa wɔde akoma korɔ hyiaa mu wɔ asɔrefie, na wɔbubuu paanoo afie mu de ahosan ne akoma kronn dii wɔn aduane,",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> na wɔyii Onyankopɔn ayɛ. Na wɔwɔ animuonyam ɔman no nyinaa anim. Na Awurade de wɔn a na wɔregye wɔn nkwa kaa asafo no ho daa."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɛrekɔbɔ awia nnɔnmmiɛnsa a wɔbɔ mpaeɛ wɔ mu no, Petro ne Yohane bɔɔ anan kɔɔ asɔrefie.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na wɔso ɔbarima bi a ɔyɛ obubuani firi ne na yam a daa wɔde no bɛto asɔrefie pono a wɔfrɛ no Fɛfɛ no ano sɛ ɔnsrɛ wɔn a wɔrekɔ asɔrefie no hɔ mmɔborɔhunu adeɛ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔhunuu Petro ne Yohane sɛ wɔrekɔ asɔrefie hɔ no, ɔsrɛɛ mmɔborɔhunu adeɛ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Petro ne Yohane de wɔn ani hwɛɛ no dinn kaa sɛ: Hwɛ yɛn!",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔhwɛɛ wɔn komm susuu sɛ ɔrebɛnya wɔn hɔ biribi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Petro kaa sɛ: Dwetɛ ne sika deɛ, menni bi, na deɛ mewɔ na mede merema woɔ yi: Nasareni Yesu Kristo din mu, nante!",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔsɔɔ ne nsa nifa maa no so, na amonom hɔ ara ne nan ne ne nanpɔso yɛɛ den.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔhuri gyinae, na ɔnantee, na ɔne wɔn kɔɔ asɔrefie hɔ a ɔnam, ɔrehurihuri na ɔreyi Onyankopɔn ayɛ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔman no nyinaa hunuu no sɛ ɔnam, na ɔreyi Onyankopɔn ayɛ;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> na wɔnim sɛ ɔno ne deɛ adesrɛ nti ɔtenaa asɔrefie Pono Fɛfɛ no ano no, na deɛ ayɛ no no yɛɛ wɔn nwanwa ne ahodwiri koraa.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Berɛ a na ɔtetare Petro ne Yohane ho no, ɔman no nyinaa de mmirika bɛhyiaa wɔn nkyɛn abrannaa a wɔfrɛ no Salomo deɛ no so, na wɔn ani so yɛɛ wɔn yaa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Petro hunuiɛ no, ɔsee ɔman no sɛ: Israel mmarima, adɛn na oyi ho yɛ mo nwanwa, anaasɛ adɛn na mohwɛ yɛn haa sɛdeɛ yɛn ara yɛn tumi, anaa ɛsom pa na yɛde maa no nanteeɛ yi?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Abraham ne Isak ne Yakob Nyankopɔn, yɛn agyanom Nyankopɔn, na wahyɛ n’akoa Yesu a moyii no maeɛ, na mopoo no wɔ Pilato a ɔbuu atɛn sɛ ɔbɛgyaa no no anim no animuonyam.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na mopoo Ɔkronkronni ne Ɔteneneeni no, na mosrɛɛ sɛ wɔmfa owudifoɔ nkyɛ mo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na nkwa hene no deɛ, mokumm no. Ɔno na Onyankopɔn anyane no afiri awufoɔ mu; ɛho adansefoɔ ne yɛn.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɛnam ne din mu gyidie so, na ne din ama oyi a mohu no, na monim no yi ho ayɛ no den. Aane, gyidie a ɛnam Yesu soɔ no na ɛmaa no akwahosan yi wɔ mo nyinaa anim.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na afei, anuanom, menim sɛ nim a monnim nti na moyɛeɛ, sɛ mo mpanimfoɔ ara.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Onyankopɔn ama deɛ ɔnam n’adiyifoɔ nyinaa anomu ka too hɔ sɛ Kristo no bɛhunu amaneɛ no aba mu saa.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Enti monsakyera mo adwene, na monnane mo ho, na wɔapepa mo bɔne,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na ɛyɛ a, ahodwoɔ nna afiri Awurade anim aba, na wasoma deɛ wɔayi no asi hɔ ama mo dada no, Yesu Kristo no",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> a ɛsɛ sɛ ɔsoro gye no de kɔsi berɛ a wɔbɛhyɛ nnoɔma a Onyankopɔn nam n’adiyifoɔ kronkron anomu, firi teteete kaeɛ no nyinaa ananmu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Mose nso kaa sɛ: Odiyifoɔ a ɔte sɛ me na Awurade mo Nyankopɔn bɛma no soɔ ama mo wɔ mo nuanom mu; ɔno na montie no, sɛdeɛ ɔbɛka akyerɛ mo nyinaa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ɛbɛba sɛ ɔkra biara a ɔrentie odiyifoɔ no no, wɔbɛsɛe no afiri ne man mu.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na adiyifoɔ nyinaa a ɛfiri Samuel so, ne wɔn a wɔdi soɔ no, dodoɔ a wɔkasaeɛ, wɔn nso kaa nna yi ho asɛm.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Mone adiyifoɔ no ne apam a Onyankopɔn ne mo agyanom pameeɛ no mma, sɛ ɔka kyerɛɛ Abraham sɛ: Na w’asefoɔ mu na wɔbɛhyira asase so mmusua nyinaa.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Mo na Onyankopɔn nyanee n’akoa no, ɔsomaa no wɔ mo nkyɛn kane sɛ ɔmmɛhyira mo, sɛ ɔbɛdane mo nyinaa afiri mo bɔne ho."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na wɔrekasa akyerɛ ɔman no no, asɔfoɔ ne asɔrefie safohene ne Sadukifoɔ baa wɔn so.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɛyɛɛ wɔn ahi sɛ wɔrekyerɛkyerɛ ɔman no, na wɔreka awufoɔ mu sɔreɛ wɔ Yesu din mu,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na wɔkyeree wɔn de wɔn kɔsiee sɛ adeɛ nkye; ɛfiri sɛ na enwunu adwo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Nso wɔn a wɔtee asɛm no mu bebree gye diiɛ, na nnipa no dodoɔ bɛyɛ mpemnum.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ adeɛ kyeeɛ no, wɔn atitire ne mpanimfoɔ ne Atwerɛfoɔ bɛhyiaa Yerusalem,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na Ɔsɔfopanin Hana ne Kaiafa ne Yohane ne Aleksandro ne dodoɔ a wɔfiri ɔsɔfo panin abusua mu no ka ho.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na wɔde wɔn bɛgyinaa mfimfini bisaa wɔn sɛ: Tumi bɛn mu anaa din bɛn mu na moyɛɛ yei?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɛnna Petro a Honhom Kronkron ahyɛ no ma no ka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Ɔman atitire ne mpanimfoɔ!",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sɛ nnɛ wɔbisa yɛn ɔyarefoɔ yi yieyɛ ho asɛm, sɛ ɛdeɛn na ama no adi mu a,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> mo nyinaa ne Israel man nyinaa nhunu sɛ, Nasareni Yesu Kristo a mobɔɔ no asɛnnua mu, a Onyankopɔn nyanee no firii awufoɔ mu no din mu, ɔno mu na oyi gyina mo anim a ne ho asane yi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Oyi ne ɔboɔ a mo abantofoɔ ammuo no, na abɛdi ntweaso ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na nkwagyeɛ nni obiara mu, na nso din foforɔ nni ɔsoro ase a wɔde ama wɔ nnipa mu a ɛsɛ sɛ wɔgye yɛn nkwa wɔ mu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na wɔhunuu Petro ne Yohane akokoɔduro, na wɔtee sɛ wɔyɛ nnipa a wɔnsuaa nwoma da, na mmom wɔyɛ mpapahwekwaa no, ɛyɛɛ wɔn nwanwa, na wɔhunuu wɔn sɛ wɔne Yesu nanteeɛ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔhwɛɛ onipa a wɔasa no yadeɛ a ɔne wɔn gyina hɔ no, wɔannya hwee anka antia wɔn.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na wɔhyɛɛ wɔn sɛ wɔmfiri dwa mu hɔ mfiri adi no, wɔtuu wɔn mu agyina",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> sɛ: Ɛdeɛn na yɛbɛyɛ nnipa yi? Na wɔahunu nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ a wɔnam wɔn so ayɛ; sɛ ada adi wɔn a wɔte Yerusalem nyinaa anim, na yɛntumi nsane.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na ɛrenkɔ so ntrɛ ɔman no mu ne sɛ: Ateatea na yɛbɛteatea wɔn sɛ wɔnnka din yi ho asɛm nnkyerɛ onipa biara bio.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na wɔfrɛɛ wɔn hyɛɛ wɔn sɛ wɔnnka asɛm, nso wɔnnkyerɛkyerɛ Yesu din mu koraa.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Petro ne Yohane bua see wɔn sɛ: Sɛ ɛtene Nyankopɔn anim sɛ yɛtie mo sene Onyankopɔn a, mommu atɛn!",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na yɛn deɛ, yɛntumi, gye sɛ yɛka deɛ yɛahunu na yɛateɛ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na wɔteateaa wɔn bio no, wɔgyaa wɔn, na ɔman no nti wɔnhunu sɛdeɛ wɔbɛtwe wɔn aso, ɛfiri sɛ, ɛnam deɛ na asie no nti, wɔn nyinaa hyɛɛ Onyankopɔn animuonyam.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na onipa a wɔyɛɛ ayaresa nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ yi wɔ ne ho no adi boro mfirinhyia aduanan.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wɔgyaa wɔn no, wɔbaa wɔn ara wɔn fekuo mu, na wɔbɛkaa deɛ asɔfoɔ mpanimfoɔ ne mpanimfoɔ no ka kyerɛɛ wɔn no nyinaa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na wɔteeɛ no, wɔde akoma korɔ maa wɔn nne so maa Onyankopɔn sɛ: Awurade, wo a woyɛɛ ɔsoro ne asase ne ɛpo ne deɛ ɛwɔ mu nyinaa,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> wonam Honhom Kronkron so de yɛn agya Dawid a ɔyɛ w’akoa no ano kaa sɛ: Adɛn nti na wiase aman yɛ gyegyeegye, na amanaman susu ade hunu?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Asase so ahemfo sɔre gyina, na atitire hyia faako sɔre tia Awurade ne ne Kristo no.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na wɔhyiae ampa tiaa w’abɔfra kronkron Yesu a woasra no no, wɔne Herode ne Pontio Pilato, ne amanaman ne Israel aman,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> sɛ wɔrebɛyɛ deɛ wo nsa ne w’agyina aka ato hɔ sɛ ɛnyɛ no nyinaa.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na afei deɛ, Awurade, hwɛ wɔn ateatea, na ma wo nkoa mfa akokoɔduro nyinaa nka w’asɛm,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> berɛ a wotene wo nsa sa yadeɛ, na wonam w’akoa kronkron Yesu din so yɛ nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ ne anwanwadeɛ yi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na wɔwiee mpaebɔ no, faako a wɔhyiaeɛ hɔ wosoee, na Honhom Kronkron hyɛɛ wɔn nyinaa ma, na wɔde akokoɔduro kaa Nyankopɔn asɛm.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na wɔn mu bebree a wɔgye diiɛ no akoma ne wɔn kra yɛ baako, na wɔn mu biara nka sɛ ne nnoɔma a ɔwɔ yɛ ɔno ara dea, na ne nyinaa yɛ wɔn kwasafodeɛ.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na asomafoɔ no de tumi kɛseɛ dii Awurade Yesu wusɔreɛ ho adanseɛ, na adom kɛseɛ wɔ wɔn nyinaa so.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Nanso na obiara nni wɔn mu a biribi hia no; na wɔn a wɔwɔ asase anaa adan tontɔnee, na wɔde deɛ wɔtɔneeɛ no tiri adeɛ bae",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> de bɛguu asomafoɔ no nan ase; na wɔkyekyɛɛ mu maa obiara sɛdeɛ ɛhia no.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na Yosef a asomafoɔ no too no Barnaba, (a ne nkyerɛaseɛ ne afotuo ba) a ɔyɛ Lewini a ɔfiri Kipro man mu no",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> wɔ asase bi, na ɔtɔnee de ne sika no ba bɛguu asomafoɔ no nan ase."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɔbarima bi a ne din de Anania ne ne yere Safira kɔtɔnee asase bi,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> na ɔyii tiri adeɛ no bi sieeɛ, a ne yere nso nim, na ɔde ɔfa bi brɛɛ asomafoɔ no.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Petro kaa sɛ: Anania, adɛn nti na Satan ahyɛ w’akoma ma sɛ bɛdi atorɔ kyerɛ Honhom Kronkron, na woayi asase no tiri adeɛ bi asie?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛwɔ hɔ no, na ɛnyɛ wo dea? Na wotɔneeɛ no nso, ɛnni wo ara wo nsam? Adɛn na wofaa saa adwene yi? Ɛnyɛ nnipa na woadi atorɔ akyerɛ wɔn, na ɛyɛ Onyankopɔn.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Anania tee nsɛm yi no, ɔhwee ase wui. Na ehu kɛseɛ baa wɔn a wɔtee yeinom nyinaa so.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na mmeranteɛ no sɔre kyekyeree no, na wɔde no firii adi kɔsiee no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ ɛbɛyɛ nnɔnhwere mmiɛnsa akyiri no, ne yere a na ɔnnim deɛ asie no baa mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Petro bisaa no sɛ: Motɔn asase no gyee saa anaa? Ka kyerɛ me! Na ɔse: Aane, saa ara.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Petro ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Adɛn na moayɛ nokorɔ sɛ morebɛsɔ Awurade Honhom ahwɛ yi? Hwɛ, wɔn a wɔkɔsiee wo kunu no nan tiatia aboboano, na wɔbɛsoa wo nso afiri adi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na amonom hɔ ara ɔhwee ne nan ase wui. Na mmeranteɛ no ba bɛhunuu no sɛ wawuo no, wɔsoaa no firii adi kɔsiee no ne kunu nkyɛn.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ehu kɛseɛ kaa asafo mu no nyinaa ne wɔn a wɔtee yeinom nyinaa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wɔnam asomafoɔ no nsa so yɛɛ nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ ne anwanwadeɛ pii ɔman no mu. Na wɔn nyinaa de akoma korɔ wɔ Salomo abrannaa so.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na wɔn a aka no mu biara ansi ne bo sɛ ɔde ne ho bɛbɔ wɔn ho, nanso ɔman no buu wɔn kɛseɛ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na nnipa bebree a wɔgye diiɛ, mmarima ne mmaa bebree bɛkaa Awurade asafo no ho.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɛmaa wɔde ayarefoɔ firii adi baa mprama so bɛtotoo mpa ne kɛtɛ so, na sɛ Petro retwam a, ne sunsum atɔ wɔn mu bi so.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na nkuro a atwa ahyia Yerusalem ho no mu nnipa pii nso bɛhyiaa Yerusalem, de ayarefoɔ ne wɔn a ahonhom fi ha wɔn bae, na wɔsaa wɔn nyinaa yadeɛ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔsɔfo panin ne wɔn a wɔka ne ho a wɔfiri Sadukifoɔ fekuo mu no nyinaa sɔreeɛ, na anibereɛ nti,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> wɔto hyɛɛ asomafoɔ no so de wɔn kɔguu kwasafo afiase.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Awurade bɔfoɔ bɛhinii afiase no apono anadwo, na ɔde wɔn firi adi kaa sɛ:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Monkɔ nkɔgyina asɔrefie nka nkwa yi nsɛm no nyinaa nkyerɛ ɔman no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na wɔteeɛ no, wɔkɔɔ asɔrefie ahemadakye kɔkyerɛkyerɛe. Na ɔsɔfo panin ne wɔn a wɔka ne ho no bae, na wɔfrɛɛ badwafoɔ ne Israel mma mpanimfoɔ nyinaa hyiae, na wɔsoma maa wɔkɔɔ afiase hɔ sɛ wɔnkɔfa wɔn mmra.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na asomfoɔ no kɔɔ hɔ na wɔanhu wɔn afiase hɔ no, wɔsane bɛkaa",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> sɛ: Afiase no deɛ, yɛhunuu sɛ wɔato mu yie pɛpɛɛpɛ, na awɛmfoɔ no gyina akyire apono no ano; nanso yɛhiniiɛ no, yɛanhunu obiara wɔ mu.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na asɔrefie safohene ne asɔfoɔ mpanimfoɔ no tee nsɛm yi no, wɔn tirim yɛɛ wɔn keserenee wɔ ho sɛ, yei bɛyɛ deɛn nie?",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na obi ba bɛka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Hwɛ, mmarima a mode wɔn guu afiase no gyina asɔrefie rekyerɛkyerɛ ɔman no.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ɛnna ɔsafohene ne asomfoɔ no firi hɔ kɔ kɔfaa wɔn baeɛ, ɛnyɛ anibereɛ so, ɛfiri sɛ na wɔsuro ɔman no sɛ anyɛ a wɔbɛsi wɔn aboɔ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na wɔde wɔn ba bɛgyinaa wɔn dwa no mu, na ɔsɔfo panin no bisaa wɔn",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> sɛ: Yɛammara mo ketee sɛ monnkyerɛkyerɛ din yi mu anaa? Na hwɛ, mode mo nkyerɛkyerɛ yi ahyɛ Yerusalem ma, na mopɛ sɛ mode onipa yi mogya ba yɛn soɔ.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na Petro ne asomafoɔ no buaa sɛ: Ɛsɛ sɛ yɛtie Onyankopɔn mmom sene nnipa.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Yɛn agyanom Nyankopɔn nyanee Yesu a mosɛnee no dua so kumm no no;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> ɔno na Onyankopɔn maa no so kɔɔ ne nifa sɛ Ɔsafohene ne Agyenkwa, sɛ ɔmma Israel adwensakyera ne bɔne fakyɛ.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Aane, yɛn, yɛyɛ yeinom ho adansefoɔ, na saa ara nso na Honhom Kronkron a Onyankopɔn de ma wɔn a wɔtie no no yɛ.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na wɔteeɛ no, ɛtwii wɔn na wɔtuu agyina sɛ wɔbɛku wɔn.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na badwafoɔ no mu baako a ɔyɛ Farisini, a ne din de Gamaliel, a ɔyɛ mmarakyerɛni, a ɔman no nyinaa bu no sɔre hyɛɛ sɛ wɔmfa nnipa no mfiri adi kakra.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Israel mmarima, monhwɛ mo ho yie nnipa yi ho wɔ deɛ mo ne wɔn rebɛdie yi ho.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na ɛnkyɛree na Teuda a ɔyɛɛ ne ho sɛ obi sɔreeɛ, na mmarima a wɔn ano bɛyɛ sɛ ahanan de wɔn ho bɔɔ ne ho; ɔno na wɔkumm no, na wɔn a wɔtiee no nyinaa hwetee, na wɔyɛɛ ɔkwa.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Oyi akyiri no, Galileani Yuda sɔree berɛ a na wɔrekan nnipa no mu, na ɔtwee nkurɔfoɔ bebree dii n’akyi; na ɔno nso wuiɛ, na wɔn a wɔtiee no nyinaa bɔ hweteeɛ.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Na afei deɛ, mese mo sɛ: Monyi mo ho mfiri nnipa yi ho, na monnyaa wɔn! Na sɛ ebia agyina yi anaa adwuma yi firi nnipa a, ɛbɛsɛe.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na sɛ nso ɛfiri Onyankopɔn a, montumi nsɛe wɔn, na moammɛyɛ sɛ mo ne Onyankopɔn mpo na ɛreko.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na wɔtiee no, na wɔfrɛɛ asomafoɔ no bae, na wɔhwee wɔn hyɛɛ wɔn sɛ wɔnnkasa Yesu din mu, na wɔgyaa wɔn.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ɛnna wɔde anigyeɛ firii badwafoɔ no anim kɔeɛ sɛ wɔabu wɔn sɛ wɔsɛ sɛ ne din nti wɔbɔ wɔn ahohora.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na wɔannyae sɛ daa nyinaa wɔka asɛmpa no na wɔkyerɛkyerɛ wɔ asɔrefie ne afie mu sɛ Yesu ne Kristo no."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na nna no mu a asuafoɔ no redɔɔso no, huhuhuhu baa Helenifoɔ no mu tiaa Hebrifoɔ no sɛ wɔbu wɔn ani gu wɔn akunafoɔ so daa ɔhwɛ a wɔhwɛ wɔn no mu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na dummienu no frɛɛ asuafokuo no bae, na wɔkaa sɛ: Ɛmfata sɛ yɛbɛgya Nyankopɔn asɛm akɔsom apono soɔ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Enti, anuanom, mompɛ mo mu mmarima baason a wɔwɔ din pa a Honhom ne nyansa ahyɛ wɔn ma, na yɛmfa wɔn nsi adwuma yi so;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> na yɛn deɛ, yɛbɛkɔ so ara akura mpaebɔ ne anyamesɛm no som mu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na asɛm no sɔɔ nnipakuo no nyinaa ani. Na wɔyii Stefano, ɔbarima a gyidie ne Honhom Kronkron ahyɛ no ma, ne Filipo ne Prokoro ne Nikanor ne Timon ne Parmena ne Nikolao a ɔfiri Antiokia a wadane Yudani.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Yeinom na wɔde wɔn gyinaa asomafoɔ no anim, na wɔsɔree de wɔn nsa guu wɔn so.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Nyankopɔn asɛm no kɔɔ so, na asuafoɔ no dɔree pii wɔ Yerusalem, na asɔfoɔ no mu pii nso yɛɛ setie maa gyidie no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Stefano a gyidie ne tumi ahyɛ no ma no yɛɛ anwanwadeɛ ne nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ akɛseɛ ɔman no mu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na nnipa bi a wɔfiri hyiadan a wɔfrɛ no Fawohodiefoɔ Hyiadan ne Kirenefoɔ ne Aleksandriafoɔ ne wɔn a wɔfiri Kilikia ne Asia sɔreeɛ, na wɔne Stefano gyee akyinnyeɛ,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> nanso wɔantumi annyina nyansa ne honhom a ɔde kasaeɛ no ano.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɛnna wɔne nnipa bi hyehyɛ maa wɔkaa sɛ: Yɛate sɛ ɔkaa abususɛm tiaa Mose ne Onyankopɔn.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wɔhwanyann ɔman no ne mpanimfoɔ ne Atwerɛfoɔ no mu, na wɔbaa ne so bɛkyeree no twee no kɔɔ dwa mu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na wɔde adansekurumfoɔ bɛgyinaa hɔ a wɔse: Onipa yi nnyaee abususɛm a ɔka tia kronkronbea hɔ ne mmara no.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na yɛate sɛ ɔkaa sɛ: Yesu Nasareni yi bɛsɛe ha, na wasakyera amanneɛ a Mose de ama yɛn no.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na wɔn a wɔte dwa mu hɔ no nyinaa hwɛɛ no dinn, na wɔhunuu sɛ n’anim te sɛ ɔsoro bɔfoɔ bi anim."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɔsɔfo panin no bisaa sɛ: Nsɛm yi te saa anaa?",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Stefano buaa sɛ: Anuanom ne agyanom, monyɛ aso! Animuonyam Nyankopɔn yii ne ho kyerɛɛ yɛn agya Abraham berɛ a ɔwɔ Mesopotamia ansa na ɔrebɛtena Haran no,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Firi w’asase so ne w’abusua mu, na bra asase a mɛkyerɛ woɔ no so!",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛnna ɔfirii Kaldeafoɔ asase so bɛtenaa Haran; na n’agya wuo akyiri no, ɔmaa no firii hɔ bɛtenaa asase yi a mote soɔ nnɛ yi so.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na wamma no agyapadeɛ wɔ mu, wamma no anammɔn baako mpo; na ɔhyɛɛ no bɔ sɛ ɔde bɛma ɔno ne n’asefoɔ a wɔdi n’akyire sɛ wɔmfa nyɛ wɔn deɛ, nanso na ɔnnya nnyaa ɔba.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na deɛ Onyankopɔn kaeɛ ne sɛ: N’asefoɔ bɛyɛ ahɔhoɔ ananafoɔ asase so, na wɔde wɔn ayɛ nkoa, na wɔayɛ wɔn bɔne mfirinhyia ahanan.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔman a wɔbɛsom wɔn sɛ nkoa no na Onyankopɔn kaa no wɔn ho sɛ: Mɛbu wɔn atɛn, na ɛno akyiri no, wɔafiri hɔ abɛsom me wɔ ha.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔmaa no twetiatwa apam. Na ɔwoo Isak, na ne nnawɔtwe soɔ no, ɔtwaa no twetia, na Isak woo Yakob, na Yakob woo agyanom mpanimfoɔ dummienu no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na agyanom mpanimfoɔ no de nitan tɔnn Yosef kɔɔ Misraim, nanso Onyankopɔn dii n’akyi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɔyii no firii n’amanehunu nyinaa mu na ɔmaa no adom ne nyansa Farao a ɔyɛ Misraim hene no anim, na ɔde no sii Misraim ne ne fie nyinaa so amrado.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɛkɔm baa Misraim ne Kanaan asase nyinaa so, ɛne ahohia kɛseɛ nso, na yɛn agyanom nnya aduane.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Yakob tee sɛ aduane wɔ Misraim no, ɔsomaa yɛn agyanom kane.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na deɛ ɛtɔ so mmienu no, Yosef yii ne ho kyerɛɛ ne nuanom, na Farao nso hunuu Yosef abusuafoɔ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Yosef soma maa wɔkɔhyiaa n’agya Yakob ne n’abusua nyinaa a wɔyɛ nnipa aduɔson nnum no bae.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Yakob kɔɔ Misraim, na ɔno ne yɛn agyanom wuwui,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> na wɔde wɔn baa Sekem bɛtotoo ɛda a Abraham de sika tɔ firii Hamor mma nkyɛn wɔ Sekem no mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɛbɔ a Onyankopɔn kaa ho ntam kyerɛɛ Abraham no berɛ reduru no, ɔman no dɔree, na wɔyɛɛ bebree wɔ Misraim",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> kɔsii sɛ ɔhene foforɔ bi a ɔnnim Yosef sɔreeɛ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ɔno na ɔde aniteɛ hyɛɛ yɛn nkurɔfoɔ soɔ, na ɔyɛɛ yɛn agyanom bɔne, na ɔmaa wɔtotoo wɔn mma nkɔkoaa gui, na ama wɔannya nkwa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ɛberɛ no ara mu na wɔwoo Mose, na ne ho yɛ fɛ Nyankopɔn anim, na wɔhwɛɛ no abosome mmiɛnsa n’agya fie.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na wɔtoo no tweneeɛ no, Farao babaa kɔfaa no, na ɔtetee no de no yɛɛ ne ba.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na wɔkyerɛɛ Mose Misraimfoɔ nyansa nyinaa, na ɔyɛɛ den wɔ ne nsɛm ne nneyɛɛ mu.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ɔdii mfirinhyia aduanan no, ɛbaa n’akomam sɛ ɔbɛkɔ akɔhwɛ ne nuanom Israel mma no.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ɔhunuu obi a wɔreyɛ no bɔne no, ɔgyee ne ti, na ɔtɔɔ deɛ wɔrehyɛ no soɔ no were kumm Misraimni no.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɔsusuu sɛ anuanom no bɛhunu sɛ Onyankopɔn nam ne nsa so rebɛgye wɔn; nanso wɔanhunu.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, ɔbɛtoo wɔn sɛ wɔreko. Ɛnna ɔpataa wɔn kaa sɛ: Mmarima, moyɛ anuanom; adɛn nti na moreyɛ mo ho bɔne?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na deɛ ɔreyɛ ne yɔnko bɔne no summ no kaa sɛ: Hwan na ɔde wo sii yɛn so panin ne temmufoɔ?",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Wopɛ sɛ wokum me, sɛdeɛ nnora wokumm Misraimni no anaa?",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na asɛm yi nti Mose dwaneeɛ, na ɔkɔyɛɛ ɔhɔhoɔ Midian asase so, na ɔwoo mmabanin baanu wɔ hɔ.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na mfirinhyia aduanan duruiɛ no, Awurade bɔfoɔ yii ne ho kyerɛɛ no wɔ serɛ so, Sinai bepɔ ho, wɔ wura bi gyaframa mu.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na Mose hunuiɛ no, anisoadeɛ no yɛɛ no nwanwa; na ɔtwe bɛnee sɛ ɔrekɔhwɛ no, Awurade nne baa sɛ:",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Mene w’agyanom Nyankopɔn, Abraham ne Isak ne Yakob Nyankopɔn. Na Mose ho popoeɛ, na wansi ne bo ankɔhwɛ.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na Awurade ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Yi wo nan mu mpaboa; na deɛ wogyina yi yɛ asase kronkron.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hunu na mahunu me man a ɛwɔ Misraim no amanehunu, na mate n’apinisie, na masiane sɛ merebɛgye wɔn; na afei bra na mensoma wo, na kɔ Misraim!",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Mose yi ara a wɔpaa no sɛ: Hwan na ɔde wo sii ɔpanin ne ɔtemmufoɔ no, ɔno ara na Onyankopɔn nam ɔbɔfoɔ a ɔyii ne ho kyerɛɛ no wɔ wura no mu no nsa soɔ somaa no sɛ ɔpanin ne ɔgyefoɔ.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ɔno ara na ɔde wɔn firii adi yɛɛ anwanwadeɛ ne nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ Misraim asase so, ne Mmɛwa Po mu ne ɛserɛ so mfirinhyia aduanan.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Oyi ne Mose a ɔka kyerɛɛ Israel mma sɛ: Odiyifoɔ a ɔte sɛ me na Onyankopɔn bɛma no so mo nuanom mu ama mo.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Oyi ne deɛ na ɔne ɔbɔfoɔ no wɔ asafo no mu ɛserɛ so hɔ a ɔbɔfoɔ no ne no ne yɛn agyanom kasaa Sinai bepɔ soɔ, na ɔgyee nkwa nsɛm no de brɛɛ yɛn no.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na yɛn agyanom nso ampɛ sɛ wɔtie no, na wɔsumm no twenee, na wɔdanee wɔn akoma kɔɔ Misraim,",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> na wɔka kyerɛɛ Aaron sɛ: Yɛ anyame a wɔbɛdi yɛn anim ma yɛn! Na Mose a ɔde yɛn firi Misraim baeɛ yi deɛ, yɛnnim deɛ ayɛ no.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ɛnna wɔyɛɛ nantwie ba, nna no mu, na wɔbɔɔ afɔdeɛ maa ohoni no, na wɔn ani gyee wɔn nsa ano adwuma ho.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na Onyankopɔn yii n’ani, na ɔde wɔn maa sɛ wɔnsom ɔsoro asafo, sɛdeɛ wɔatwerɛ adiyifoɔ nwoma no mu sɛ: Israel fiefoɔ, mode mmoa ne nnuane bɔɔ afɔdeɛ maa me mfirinhyia aduanan ɛserɛ so anaa?",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Mmom mofaa Molok ntomadan ne onyame Refan nsoromma, ahoni a moyɛeɛ sɛ mobɛsom wɔn; na mɛsoa mo akɔ Babel akyiri nohoa.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Yɛn agyanom nyaa adanseɛ ntomadan no wɔ ɛserɛ so, sɛdeɛ deɛ ɔkasa kyerɛɛ Mose no hyɛɛ no sɛ ɔnyɛ no sɛdeɛ adeɛ a ɔhunuiɛ no teɛ no.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Yɛn agyanom nsa kaa saa ntomadan yi no, wɔne Yosua de baa amanaman a Onyankopɔn pamm wɔn firii yɛn agyanom anim no asase so. Ɛte saa ara de bɛsii Dawid berɛ so.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ɔno na ɔnyaa Nyankopɔn anim adom, na ɔsrɛɛ sɛ wɔmma no nsi efie mma Yakob Nyankopɔn.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Nanso Salomo na ɔsii efie no maa no.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Mmom deɛ ɔwɔ sorosoro no nte deɛ wɔde nsa ayeyɛ mu, sɛdeɛ odiyifoɔ no ka sɛ:",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Awurade se: Ɔsoro yɛ m’ahennwa, na asase yɛ me nan ntiasoɔ; ɔdan bɛn na mobɛsi ama me? Anaasɛ ɛhe ne me homebea?",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Ɛnyɛ me nsa na ɛyɛɛ yeinom nyinaa?",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Mo a mo kɔn asene na moyɛ akoma ne aso mu momonoto, daa mo ne Honhom Kronkron di asie; sɛdeɛ mo agyanom yɛeɛ no, saa ara na moyɛ.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Adiyifoɔ no mu hwan na mo agyanom antaa no? Na wɔkumm wɔn a wɔkaa Ɔteneneeni no ba no ho asɛm kane no; ɔno na afei moayi no ama wɔaku no,",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> mo a monyaa mmara no sɛdeɛ abɔfoɔ hyɛeɛ no, nanso moanni soɔ.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Na wɔtee yeinom no, wɔn ani bereeɛ, na wɔtwɛree wɔn se guu ne so.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Nanso ɔno deɛ, na Honhom Kronkron ahyɛ no ma, na ɔhwɛɛ soro dinn hunuu Nyankopɔn animuonyam ne Yesu sɛ ɔgyina Nyankopɔn nifa,",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> na ɔkaa sɛ: Hwɛ, mehunu soro sɛ abue, na Onipa Ba no gyina Nyankopɔn nifa.",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Na wɔde nne kɛseɛ teaa mu, na wɔsisii wɔn aso, na wɔbɔɔ kirididi kɔto hyɛɛ ne so,",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> na wɔsunsumm no firii kuro no mu kɔsii no aboɔ. Na adansefoɔ no de wɔn ntoma guguu aberanteɛ bi a wɔfrɛ no Saulo nan ase.",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Na wɔresi Stefano aboɔ no, ɔsrɛɛ sɛ: Awurade Yesu, gye me honhom!",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Na ɔkotoo ne nan anim de nne kɛseɛ teaa mu sɛ: Awurade, mfa bɔne yi nto wɔn so! Na ɔkaa yei no, ɔkaa n’ani guu so."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Saulo nso, penee ne kum no so. Na da no ara ɔtaa kɛseɛ baa asafo a ɛwɔ Yerusalem no so, na wɔn nyinaa hwete kɔɔ Yudea ne Samaria nsase so, gye asomafoɔ no nko.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Nso nnipa nyamesurofoɔ bi siee Stefano, na wɔsuu no pii.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Saulo deɛ, ɔhaa asafo no, hyɛnehyɛnee afie mu, kɔtwee mmarima ne mmaa, na ɔde wɔn kɔguu afiase.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛnna wɔn a wɔhweteeɛ no kyinkyini kɔkaa asɛmpa no.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Filipo kɔɔ Samaria kuro bi mu kɔkaa Kristo ho asɛm kyerɛɛ wɔn.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na nkurɔfoɔ akuakuo no teeɛ, na wɔhunuu nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ a Filipo yɛeɛ no, wɔde akoma korɔ yɛɛ aso maa nsɛm a ɔkaeɛ no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ahonhom fi a ɛwɔ nnipa bebree mu de nne kɛseɛ teaa mu firii adi, na mmubuafoɔ ne mpakye pii ho sanee wɔn.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na anigyeɛ kɛseɛ baa kuro no mu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔbarima bi a ɔde Simon wɔ kuro no mu a akane no na ɔyi nkonyaa, na ɔyɛ ne ho sɛ obi a ɔyɛ kɛseɛ maa Samariafoɔ no ho dwirii wɔn.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɔno na wɔn nyinaa, ɛfiri nketewa soɔ kɔsi akɛseɛ soɔ tie no ka sɛ: Oyi ne Nyankopɔn tumi a wɔfrɛ no Kɛseɛ no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Wɔtiee no, ɛfiri sɛ na ɔde nkonyaayie no ama wɔn ho adwiri wɔn akyɛ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wɔgyee Filipo a ɔka Nyankopɔn ahennie ne Yesu Kristo din ho asɛmpa no diiɛ no, mmarima ne mmaa no maa wɔbɔɔ wɔn asu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Simon no ara nso gye dii, na wɔbɔɔ no asu no, ɔde ne ho bataa Filipo ho; na ɔhunuu nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ ne ahoɔdenneɛ akɛseɛ a ɔyɛeɛ no, ne ho dwirii no.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na asomafoɔ a wɔwɔ Yerusalem no tee sɛ Samariafoɔ agye Nyankopɔn asɛm no, wɔsomaa Petro ne Yohane kɔɔ wɔn nkyɛn.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na wɔbaeɛ no, wɔbɔɔ mpaeɛ maa wɔn sɛ wɔnnya Honhom Kronkron;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ɛfiri sɛ na ɔmmaa wɔn mu biara so, na asu nko na wɔabɔ wɔn akɔ Awurade Yesu din mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛnna wɔde wɔn nsa guu wɔn soɔ, na wɔnyaa Honhom Kronkron.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Simon hunuu sɛ ɛnam asomafoɔ no nsa a wɔde gu obi soɔ no so na wɔde Honhom no ma no, ɔde sika brɛɛ wɔn kaa sɛ:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Momma me tumi yi bi, na obiara a mede me nsa bɛgu ne soɔ no, wanya Honhom Kronkron.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na Petro ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Wo ne wo sika nyinaa nyera, ɛfiri sɛ woasusu sɛ wɔde sika na ɛnya Nyankopɔn akyɛdeɛ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Wonni asɛm yi mu kyɛfa anaa apɛgyadeɛ, ɛfiri sɛ w’akoma ntene Nyankopɔn anim.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Enti sakyera w’adwene firi wo bɔne yi ho, na srɛ Onyankopɔn sɛ ebia wɔde w’akoma mu adwene no bɛkyɛ wo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ mahunu sɛ wowɔ bɔnwoma nwononwono mu, na amumuyɛ homa akyekyere wo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na Simon buaa sɛ: Monsrɛ Awurade mma me, na deɛ moaka yi mu biara amma me so.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na wɔn deɛ, wɔdii adanseɛ na wɔkaa Awurade asɛm no, wɔsane kɔɔ Yerusalem, na wɔkaa asɛmpa no wɔ Samariafoɔ nkuraa bebree ase.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na Awurade bɔfoɔ kasa kyerɛɛ Filipo sɛ: Sɔre kɔ anafoɔ fam kwan a ɛsiane firi Yerusalem kɔ Gasa no so! Ɛyɛ anwea pradada so kwan.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ɔsɔre kɔe. Na hwɛ, Etiopiani barima bi a ɔyɛ Etiopiafoɔ hemmaa Kandake piani tumfoɔ a wɔasa no, a ɔhwɛ ne sika nyinaa soɔ ni; waba Yerusalem abɛsɔre,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> na ɔresane akorɔ, na ɔte ne teaseɛnam mu rekenkan Odiyifoɔ Yesaia nwoma.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na Honhom no ka kyerɛɛ Filipo sɛ: Twe kɔ teaseɛnam yi ho!",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na Filipo de mmirika kɔɔ ne nkyɛn, na ɔtee sɛ ɔrekenkan Odiyifoɔ Yesaia nwoma no, ɔbisaa no sɛ: Wote deɛ worekenkan yi ase anaa?",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na ɔse: Ɛbɛyɛ dɛn na mɛtumi, gye sɛ obi kyerɛ me? Na ɔsrɛɛ Filipo sɛ ɔmforo mmɛtena ne nkyɛn.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Nso atwerɛ no mu asɛm a ɔrekenkan no nie: Wɔde no kɔɔ sɛ odwanten a wɔrekɔku no, na sɛ adwammaa tɔ ne yifoɔ anim mum no, sɛ nso wammue n’ano ne no.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> N’ahobrɛaseɛ mu wɔbuu no ntɛnkyea. N’abusua nso hwan na ɔbɛtumi akyerɛ? Ɛfiri sɛ wɔyii ne nkwa firii asase so.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na opiani no buaa Filipo sɛ: Mesrɛ wo, hwan ho asɛm na odiyifoɔ no reka yi? Ɔno ara anaa obi ho asɛm?",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na Filipo buee n’ano, na ɔgyinaa twerɛsɛm no ara so kaa Yesu ho asɛmpa no kyerɛɛ no.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na wɔnam kwan so rekorɔ no, wɔkɔduruu asuo bi ho, na opiani no kaa sɛ: Hwɛ, nsuo ni; ɛdeɛn na ɛsi me asubɔ ho kwan?",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> [Na Filipo se: Sɛ wode w’akoma nyinaa gye di a, ɛwɔ ho kwan saa. Na ɔbuaa sɛ: Megye medi sɛ Yesu Kristo ne Nyankopɔn ba.]",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Na ɔhyɛ maa teaseɛnam no gyinae, na wɔn baanu siane kɔɔ nsuo no mu, Filipo ne opiani no, na ɔbɔɔ no asu.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na wɔfiri nsuo no mu reba no, Awurade honhom hwimm Filipo, na opiani no anhu no bio; na ɔde anigyeɛ kɔɔ ne kwan.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na Filipo deɛ, ɔkɔfirii Asoto; na ɔretwa mu no, ɔkaa asɛmpa no nkuro no nyinaa mu de kɔsii sɛ ɔduruu Kaesarea."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Saulo a ɔda so home ahunahuna ne okum home gu Awurade asuafoɔ soɔ no kɔɔ ɔsɔfo panin nkyɛn",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> kɔsrɛɛ ne nkyɛn nwoma sɛ ɔde rekɔ Damasko akɔ hyia adan mu, na sɛ ɔhunu nnipa bi saa gyidie kwan no mu a, mmarima oo, mmaa oo, ɔde wɔn homa mu aba Yerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔnam nam no, ɛbaa sɛ ɔbɛnee Damasko, na mpofirim, hann a ɛfiri soro bɛhyerɛn twaa ne ho hyiae.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔhwee fam, na ɔtee nne bi a ɛka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Saulo, Saulo, adɛn na wotaa me?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɛnna ɔse: Ɛyɛ wo hwan a, Awurade? Na ɔse: Ɛyɛ me Yesu a wotaa no no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Sɔre kɔ kuro no mu, na wɔbɛka wo deɛ ɛsɛ sɛ woyɛ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na mmarima a wɔne no nam no atotɔre mum gyinagyina hɔ, wɔtee nne no deɛ, nanso wɔanhunu obiara.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Saulo sɔre firii fam, na ɔbuee n’ani no, wanhunu hwee. Na wɔkurakuraa ne nsa de no kɔɔ Damasko.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na nnansa na ɔnhunu adeɛ, nso ɔnnidi na ɔnnom.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na osuani bi wɔ Damasko a ne din de Anania. Na Awurade ka kyerɛɛ no anisoadehunu mu sɛ: Anania! Na ɔse: Hwɛ, meni, Awurade!",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Awurade ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Sɔre kɔ borɔno a wɔfrɛ no Turodoo no so, na kɔbisa obi a wɔfrɛ no Saulo a ɔfiri Tarso no akyiri kwan wɔ Yuda fie; na hwɛ, ɔrebɔ mpaeɛ,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> na wahunu ɔbarima bi a ɔde Anania anisoadehunu mu sɛ ɔreba ne nkyɛn, na ɔde ne nsa ato ne so sɛ ɔnhunu adeɛ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Anania buaa sɛ: Awurade, mate ɔbarima yi ho asɛm afiri nnipa bebree anomu sɛ ɔde bɔne pii ayɛ w’ahotefoɔ wɔ Yerusalem,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na ɛha yi nso wanya tumi afiri asɔfoɔ mpanimfoɔ no nsam sɛ ɔnkyere wɔn a wɔbɔ wo din nyinaa.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ɛnna Awurade ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Kɔ ara, na oyi ne adwumadeɛ a mayi no a ɔbɛsoa me din akɔ amanaman ne ahemfo ne Israel mma anim.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na me na mɛkyerɛ no amaneɛ pii a me din nti ɛsɛ sɛ ɔhunu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Anania kɔ kɔhyɛnee ɔdan no mu, na ɔde ne nsa kɔguu ne so kaa sɛ: Onua Saulo, Awurade Yesu a ɔyii ne ho kyerɛɛ wo kwan a wonam so reba ha no, wasoma me sɛ hunu adeɛ, na Honhom Kronkron nhyɛ wo ma.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ntɛm ara na biribi a ɛte sɛ abon firii n’ani so guu fam, na amonom hɔ ara ɔhunuu adeɛ, na ɔsɔre maa wɔbɔɔ no asu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔdidiiɛ no, ne ho yɛɛ no den. Na ɔdii asuafoɔ a wɔwɔ Damasko no nkyɛn nna kakra.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na ntɛm ara ɔkaa Yesu ho asɛm hyia adan mu sɛ ɔne Nyankopɔn ba no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na wɔn a wɔteeɛ nyinaa ho dwirii wɔn, na wɔse: Ɛnyɛ oyi ne deɛ na ɔsɛe wɔn a wɔbɔ din yi wɔ Yerusalem, na yei nti ɔbaa ha sɛ ɔrebɛfa wɔn homa mu akɔma asɔfoɔ mpanimfoɔ no anaa?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Saulo kɔɔ so ara nyaa ahoɔden, na ɔmaa Yudafoɔ a wɔte Damasko no ho yeraa wɔn, na ɔdii adanseɛ kyerɛɛ sɛ Yesu ne Kristo no.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na nna bebree akyiri no, Yudafoɔ no pamm ne tiri so sɛ wɔbɛkum no.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Nanso Saulo tee wɔn agyina no. Na wɔwɛnee kuro no apono ano awia ne anadwo sɛ wɔbɛku no.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na n’asuafoɔ no faa no anadwo, de no too kɛntɛnku mu, faa ɔfasuo so, twetwee no sii fam.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na ɔduruu Yerusalem no, ɔpɛɛ sɛ ɔde ne ho kɔbɔ asuafoɔ no ho; nanso na wɔn nyinaa suro no, ɛfiri sɛ wɔannye anni sɛ ɔyɛ osuani.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na Barnaba faa no ne no kɔɔ asomafoɔ no nkyɛn, na ɔdaa no adi kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛdeɛ ɔhunuu Awurade ɔkwan mu ne sɛ ɔkasa kyerɛɛ no, ne sɛdeɛ ɔde akokoɔduro kaa Yesu ho asɛm wɔ Damasko.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na ɔne wɔn dii ahyemfire wɔ Yerusalem, na ɔde nnam kaa Awurade din ho asɛm.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na ɔkasa kyerɛɛ Helenifoɔ no, na ɔne wɔn gyee akyinnyeɛ; na wɔhwehwɛɛ sɛ wɔku no.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na anuanom no teɛɛ no, wɔde no siane kɔɔ Kaesarea, na wɔgyaa no kwan maa no kɔɔ Tarso.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ɛnna asafo no nyaa asomdwoeɛ Yudea ne Galilea ne Samaria nyinaa, na wɔnyini kɔɔ so; na wɔnam Awurade suro ne Honhom Kronkron awerɛkyekyerɛ mu dɔree.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ Petro kyinkyinii wɔn nyinaa soɔ no, ɔbaa ahotefoɔ a wɔte Lida no nso nkyɛn.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na ɔbɛhunuu onipa bi a ne din de Aenea a wadi mfirinhyia nwɔtwe ne kɛtɛ so, a ɔyare mmubuo wɔ hɔ.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na Petro ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Aenea, Yesu Kristo sa wo yadeɛ. Sɔre, na wo ara sɛ wo kɛtɛ! Na ɔsɔree ntɛm ara.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na wɔn a wɔte Lida ne Saron nyinaa hunuu no, na wɔdane baa Awurade nkyɛn.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Nso na osuani baa bi wɔ Yopa a ne din de Tabita a ne nkyerɛaseɛ ne Dorka. Ɔbaa yi na nnwuma pa ne mmɔborɔhunu adeɛ a ɔyɛeɛ no ayɛ no ma.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ nna no mu no, ɔyaree, na ɔwuiɛ; na wɔdwaree no de no kɔtoo abansoro dan mu.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Nso Lida bɛn Yopa nti, asuafoɔ no tee sɛ Petro wɔ hɔ no, wɔsomaa nnipa baanu kɔɔ ne nkyɛn kɔsrɛɛ no sɛ ɔnntwentwɛn ne nan ase, na ɔmmra wɔn nkyɛn.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na Petro sɔre ne wɔn kɔeɛ. Na ɔduruu hɔ no, wɔde no kɔɔ abansoro dan no mu, na akunafoɔ no nyinaa bɛgyinaa ne ho a wɔresu, na wɔde ntadeɛ ne ntoma a na Dorka ne wɔn wɔ hɔ no ɔyɛeɛ no kyerɛe.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na Petro pamoo wɔn nyinaa firii adie no, ɔkotoo ne nan anim bɔɔ mpaeɛ, na ɔdanee n’ani kyerɛɛ amu no, na ɔse: Tabita, sɔre! Na ɔtee n’ani, na ɔhunuu Petro no, ɔsɔre tenaa ase.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Na ɔtenee ne nsa de maa no so; na ɔfrɛɛ ahotefoɔ ne akunafoɔ no de no anikan kyerɛɛ wɔn.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na wɔtee no wɔ Yopa nyinaa, na nnipa bebree gyee Awurade dii.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Na ɔtenaa Yopa kyɛree kakra wɔ Simon nwomahyɛni bi nkyɛn."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɔbarima bi wɔ Kaesarea a ne din de Kornelio; ɔyɛ asraafokuo a wɔfrɛ no Italia deɛ no mu ɔha so panin.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ɔyɛ onyamesuroni a ɔne ne fiefoɔ nyinaa suro Onyankopɔn, na ɔyɛ mmɔborɔhunu adeɛ bebree ma nkurɔfoɔ no, na ɔbɔ Onyankopɔn mpaeɛ daa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ɛbɛyɛ awia nnɔnmmiɛnsa no, ɔhunuu anisoadeɛ pefee sɛ Nyankopɔn bɔfoɔ baa ne nkyɛn bɛsee no sɛ: Kornelio!",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔhwɛɛ no dinn, na ɔsuroe. Na ɔse: Ɛyɛ deɛn, Awura? Na ɔsee no sɛ: Wo mpaebɔ ne wo mmɔborɔhunu adeɛ no aforo soro abɛyɛ nkaeɛ adeɛ wɔ Onyankopɔn anim.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na afei soma nnipa kɔ Yopa kɔhyia Simon a wɔfrɛ no Petro.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɔte Simon, nwomahyɛni bi a ne fie wɔ mpoano no nkyɛn.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔbɔfoɔ a ɔkasa kyerɛɛ no no kɔeɛ no, ɔfrɛɛ ne fie nnipa baanu ne ɔsraani nyamesuroni bi a ɔfiri wɔn a wɔsom no daa no mu,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na ɔkaa ne nyinaa kyerɛɛ wɔn no, ɔsomaa wɔn kɔɔ Yopa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ na wɔnam kwan so rebɛn kuro no no, Petro kɔɔ aban atifi kɔbɔɔ mpaeɛ, ɛbɛyɛ awia dummienu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɛkɔm de no sɛ, na ɔpɛɛ sɛ ɔde biribi ka n’ano; na wɔresiesie aduane no, n’ani wiaa no maa ɔkɔɔ tebea foforɔ mu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔhunuu soro sɛ abue, na adeɛ bi a ɛte sɛ nwera kɛseɛ a wɔakyekyere no ahinanan resiane aba ne soɔ, na wɔregyaa mu ato fam.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Emu na asase so ntɔteboa ne wɔn a wɔwea ne wiem ntakraboa nyinaa bi wɔ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɛnne bi baa ne nkyɛn sɛ: Petro, sɔre kum di!",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Petro se: Dabi da, Awurade, ɛfiri sɛ mennii biribi a wɔkyire anaasɛ ɛho nteɛ da.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɛnne no sane baa ne nkyɛn ne mprenu so sɛ: Deɛ Onyankopɔn ate ho no, mmu no akyiwadeɛ!",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na yei yɛɛ mprɛnsa, na wɔfaa adeɛ no kɔɔ soro bio.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Petro regye ne mu akyinnyeɛ sɛ anisoadeɛ a ɔhunuiɛ no ase ne sɛn no, hwɛ, na nnipa a Kornelio somaa wɔn no abisa Simon fie kwan, gyinagyina aboboano",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> refrɛ, na wɔbisaa sɛ: Simon a wɔfrɛ no Petro no te ha anaa?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Petro redwene anisoadeɛ no ho no, Honhom no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Hwɛ, nnipa baasa bi rehwehwɛ wo;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na sɔre si fam, na wo ne wɔn nkɔ; nnye akyinnyeɛ, na me na mesomaa wɔn.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Petro siane kɔɔ nnipa a Kornelio somaa wɔn baa ne nkyɛn no nkyɛn kaa sɛ: Hwɛ, mene deɛ morehwehwɛ no no; ɛdeɛn nti na mobaeɛ?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na wɔbuaa sɛ: Asraafoɔ ɔha so panin Kornelio, onipa tenenee a ɔsuro Onyankopɔn na ɔwɔ din pa Yudafoɔ man nyinaa mu, ɔno na ɔbɔfoɔ kronkron bi yi kyerɛɛ no sɛ ɔmmɛfrɛ wo mmra ne fie, na ɔntie w’anomu nsɛm.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ɛnna ɔfrɛɛ wɔn baa fie yɛɛ wɔn hɔhoɔ. Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, Petro ne wɔn firi kɔe, na anuanom a wɔwɔ Yopa no mu bi ne no kɔe.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, wɔduruu Kaesarea; na Kornelio afrɛfrɛ n’abusuafoɔ ne ne nnamfo a wɔbɛn no ahyia retwɛn.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Petro fitiiɛ ara pɛ na Kornelio kɔhyiaa no hwee ne nan ase sɔree no.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na Petro maa no so kaa sɛ: Sɔre, na me nso meyɛ onipa.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ɔne no redi nkɔmmɔ no, ɔhyɛnee mu, na ɔkɔhunuu nnipa bebree a wɔahyia hɔ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Mo ara monim sɛdeɛ Yudani nni ho kwan sɛ ɔde ne ho bɔ ɔnanani ho, anaasɛ ɔkɔ ne nkyɛn; na me deɛ, Onyankopɔn akyerɛ me sɛ memmfrɛ onipa biara sɛ ɔmfra, anaasɛ ne ho nte.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Enti nso na mosoma maa wɔbɛhyiaa me no, manyi ano na maba yi. Afei merebisa asɛm ko a enti mobɛfrɛɛ me.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na Kornelio se: Nnanan ni, bɛyɛ dɔn yi mu, na merebɔ nnɔnmmiɛnsa mu mpaeɛ wɔ me fie; na hwɛ, ɔbarima bi a ɔhyɛ atadeɛ a ɛhran bɛgyinaa m’anim,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> na ɔse: Kornelio, wɔate wo mpaebɔ, na wɔakae wo mmɔborɔhunu adeɛ no Nyankopɔn anim.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Enti soma kɔ Yopa kɔhyia Simon a wɔfrɛ no Petro; ɔte nwomahyɛni Simon fie wɔ mpoano.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Enti ntɛm ara mesoma baa wo nkyɛn; na wo nso, woayɛ no yie sɛ woaba. Na afei yɛn nyinaa ahyia Nyankopɔn anim sɛ yɛrebɛtie deɛ Onyankopɔn ahyɛ woɔ nyinaa.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na Petro buee n’ano kaa sɛ: Nokorɛ mu na mahunu sɛ Onyankopɔn nhwɛ onipa anim,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> na mmom ɔman biara mu deɛ ɔsuro no, na ɔyɛ ade tenenee no, ɔpɛ sɛ ɔgye no.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Sɛdeɛ asɛm a ɔde brɛɛ Israel mma berɛ a ɔnam Yesu Kristo so kaa asomdwoeɛ ho asɛmpa no teɛ no; ɔno ne nnipa nyinaa wura.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Mo ara monim asɛm a asubɔ a Yohane kaa ho asɛm no akyi, ɛfirii aseɛ Galilea na ɛbaa Yudea nyinaa no,",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Yesu a ɔfiri Nasaret, sɛdeɛ Onyankopɔn de Honhom Kronkron ne tumi sraa no, na ɔkyini yɛɛ yie, na ɔsaa wɔn a ɔbonsam hyɛɛ wɔn soɔ no yadeɛ, ɛfiri sɛ Onyankopɔn ka ne ho.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na yɛne nnoɔma a ɔyɛɛ no Yudafoɔ soɔ ne Yerusalem nyinaa ho adansefoɔ; ɔno nso na wɔsɛnee no dua so kumm no.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Ɔno na Onyankopɔn nyanee no da a ɛtɔ so mmiɛnsa; na ɔmaa no yii ne ho pefee kyerɛe,",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> ɛnyɛ ɔman no nyinaa, na mmom adansefoɔ a Onyankopɔn ayi wɔn ato hɔ dada no, ɛne yɛn a ne sɔreɛ a ɔsɔre firii awufoɔ mu no akyiri no, yɛne no didiiɛ na yɛnomeeɛ;",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> na ɔhyɛɛ yɛn sɛ yɛnka nkyerɛ ɔman no, na yɛnni adanseɛ sɛ ɔno ne ateasefoɔ ne awufoɔ temmufoɔ a Onyankopɔn ayi no asi hɔ no.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Ɔno na adiyifoɔ nyinaa di ne ho adanseɛ sɛ: Obiara a ɔgye no die no nam ne din so bɛnya bɔne fakyɛ.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Na Petro gu so reka nsɛm yi no, Honhom Kronkron bɛguu wɔn a wɔtee asɛm no nyinaa so.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Na agyidifoɔ a wɔfiri twetiatwafoɔ mu a wɔne Petro baeɛ no ho dwirii wɔn sɛ wɔahwie Honhom Kronkron akyɛdeɛ no agu amanaman mufoɔ nso soɔ;",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> ɛfiri sɛ wɔtee sɛ wɔde tɛkyerɛma foforɔ rekasa, na wɔreyi Onyankopɔn ayɛ kɛse. Ɛnna Petro buaa sɛ:",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Obi bɛtumi asi nsuo ho kwan sɛ wɔmmmɔ yeinom a wɔanya Honhom Kronkron sɛ yɛn ara yi asu anaa?",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Na ɔhyɛɛ sɛ wɔmmɔ wɔn asu Awurade din mu. Ɛnna wɔsrɛɛ no sɛ ɔntena wɔn nkyɛn nnansa bi."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na asomafoɔ ne anuanom a wɔwɔ Yudea no tee sɛ amanaman mufoɔ no nso agye Nyankopɔn asɛm.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Petro baa Yerusalem no, wɔn a wɔyɛ twetiatwafoɔ no ne no gyee akyinnyeɛ",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> sɛ: Adɛn nti na woakɔ nnipa a wɔnyɛ twetiatwafoɔ mu, na wo ne wɔn akɔdidie yi?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Petro firii aseɛ bɔɔ wɔn ne nyinaa ho amanneɛ mmaako mmaako sɛ:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Mewɔ Yopa kuro mu merebɔ mpaeɛ, na m’ani wiaa me maa mekɔɔ tebea foforɔ mu, na anisoadehunu mu no, mehunuu biribi a ɛresiane sɛ nwera kɛseɛ a wɔakyekyere no ahinanan, na wɔgyaa mu firi soro, na ɛbaa me nkyɛn.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na megyenee m’ani mehwɛɛ mu no, mehunuu asase so ntɔteboa ne anwonanwonammoa ne wɔn a wɔwea ne wiem ntakraboa wɔ mu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na metee sɛ ɛnne bi ka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Petro, sɔre kum di!",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na mese: Dabi da, Awurade, ɛfiri sɛ biribiara a wɔkyire, anaa ɛho nteɛ nkɔɔ m’anomu da.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɛnne no firi soro buaa me ne mprenu so sɛ: Deɛ Onyankopɔn ate ho no, mmu no akyiwadeɛ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Yei yɛɛ mprɛnsa, na wɔtwetwee ne nyinaa kɔɔ soro bio.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na amonom hɔ ara na nnipa baasa a wɔsomaa wɔn firi Kaesarea baa me nkyɛn no gyina efie a mewɔ mu no ano.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Honhom no ka kyerɛɛ me sɛ me ne wɔn nkɔ, na mennye hwee ho akyinnyeɛ. Nso anuanom baasia yi ne me kɔe, na yɛkɔɔ ɔbarima no fie.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔkaa yɛn sɛdeɛ ɔhunuu ɔbɔfoɔ sɛ ɔgyina ne fie hɔ, na ɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Soma nnipa kɔ Yopa kɔhyia Simon a wɔfrɛ no Petro.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ɔno na ɔbɛka nsɛm a wo ne wo fie nyinaa nam so bɛnya nkwagyeɛ akyerɛ woɔ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na mefirii aseɛ sɛ merekasa no, Honhom Kronkron bɛguu wɔn so, sɛdeɛ mfitiaseɛ no, ɛbɛguu yɛn so no ara.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na mekaee Awurade asɛm a ɔkaa sɛ: Yohane de nsuo na ɛbɔɔ asu, na mo deɛ, wɔde Honhom Kronkron na ɛbɛbɔ mo asu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Enti sɛ Onyankopɔn maa wɔn akyɛdeɛ korɔ no ara sɛ yɛn nso a yɛgyee Awurade Yesu Kristo diiɛ no a, mene hwan a mɛtumi masi Onyankopɔn kwan?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na wɔtee nsɛm yi no, wɔmuaa wɔn ano, na wɔyii Onyankopɔn ayɛ sɛ: Ɛnneɛ na Onyankopɔn ama amanaman mufoɔ no nso adwensakyera a ɛde kɔ nkwa mu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Afei wɔn a ɔhaw a ɛsɔree Stefano soɔ no nti wɔhweteeɛ no kyinii kɔduruu Foinike ne Kipro ne Antiokia, na wɔanka asɛm no ankyerɛ obiara sɛ Yudafoɔ nko.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na wɔn mu binom nso a wɔyɛ Kiprofoɔ ne Kirenefoɔ baa Antiokia no, wɔkasa kaa Awurade Yesu ho asɛmpa kyerɛɛ Helafoɔ no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Awurade nsa ka wɔn ho, na nnipa pii gye dii, na wɔdane baa Awurade nkyɛn.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na wɔn ho asɛm yi duruu asafo a ɛwɔ Yerusalem no aso mu, na wɔsomaa Barnaba sɛ ɔnkɔ ara nkɔduru Antiokia.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ɔbaeɛ na ɔbɛhunuu Nyankopɔn adom no, n’ani gyee, na ɔtuu wɔn nyinaa fo sɛ wɔnsi wɔn adwene pi mmata Awurade ho.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ɔyɛ onipa pa a Honhom Kronkron ne gyidie ahyɛ no ma. Na wɔde nkurɔfoɔ bebree bɛkaa Awurade ho.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɔfiri hɔ kɔɔ Tarso kɔhwehwɛɛ Saulo;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> na ɔhunuu no no, ɔde no baa Antiokia. Na wɔne asafo no bɛtenae afirinhyia mu, na wɔkyerɛkyerɛɛ nkurɔfoɔ bebree. Antiokia na wɔdii kan too asuafoɔ no din Kristofoɔ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na nna no mu no, adiyifoɔ bi firi Yerusalem baa Antiokia.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na wɔn mu baako a ne din de Agabo sɔree nam Honhom so kyerɛɛ sɛ ɛkɔm kɛseɛ rebɛba asase nyinaa so; ɛno na ɛbaa mu Klaudio berɛ soɔ no.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na asuafoɔ no bɔɔ wɔn tirim sɛ wɔn nyinaa mmaako mmaako de biribi bɛmane anuanom a wɔte Yudea no, sɛdeɛ wɔn mu biara bɛtumi, na wɔde ahwɛ wɔn.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Wɔyɛɛ saa, na wɔde somaa Barnaba ne Saulo maa wɔde kɔmaa mpanimfoɔ no."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Saa berɛ yi ara na Ɔhene Herode tenee ne nsa yɛɛ asafo no mu nnipa bi ayayadeɛ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ɔde nkrantɛ kumm Yohane nua Yakobo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔhunuu sɛ ɛsɔɔ Yudafoɔ ani nti, ɔtoaa so kɔfaa Petro nso, nanso na ɛyɛ Apiti nna;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> na ɔkyee no no, ɔde no kɔtoo afiase. Na ɔde no hyɛɛ asraafoɔ baanan a wɔwɛn bom saa ahodoɔ nnan nsa sɛ wɔnwɛn no. Na ɔpɛ sɛ Twam afahyɛ no akyiri no, ɔyi no kɔkyerɛ ɔman no.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Afei wɔde Petro kɔtoo afiase hɔ deɛ, nanso asafo no toaa so bɔɔ Onyankopɔn mpaeɛ maa no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Anadwo no ara a Herode rebɛyi no akorɔ no, na Petro da asraafoɔ baanu ntam a wɔde nkɔnsɔnkɔnsɔn mmienu agu no, na awɛmfoɔ a wɔgyinagyina ɛpono ano rewɛn afiase no anibereɛ so.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na hwɛ, Awurade bɔfoɔ bɛgyinaa ne nkyɛn, na ɛdan no mu hɔ hrann; na ɔbɔɔ Petro nkyɛn mu nyanee no sɛ: Sɔre ntɛm! Na ne nkɔnsɔnkɔnsɔn no firii ne nsa gui.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔbɔfoɔ no ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Bɔ w’abɔsoɔ na hyɛ wo mpaboa! Na ɔyɛɛ saa. Na ɔsee no sɛ: Fira wo ntoma na di m’akyi!",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔfirii adi dii n’akyi; na na ɔnnim sɛ deɛ ɔbɔfoɔ no yɛeɛ no yɛ ampa, ɛfiri sɛ ɔsusuu sɛ ɔrehunu n’ani so adeɛ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na wɔtwaa awɛmfoɔ a wɔdi kan ne wɔn a wɔtɔ so mmienu ho no, wɔduruu dadeɛ pono a ɛde kɔ kuro no mu no ho, na ɛno ara ankasa bue maa wɔn, na wɔfirii adi twaa mu borɔno baako so, na ntɛm ara ɔbɔfoɔ no gyaa no hɔ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Petro ani baa ne ho soɔ no, ɔkaa sɛ: Afei na mahunu ampa sɛ Awurade asoma ne bɔfoɔ abɛyi me afiri Herode nsam ne deɛ Yudafoɔ man retwɛn nyinaa mu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔresusu ho no, ɔbaa Yohane a wɔfrɛ no Marko ne na Maria fie; ɛhɔ na na nnipa bebree aboaboa wɔn ano rebɔ mpaeɛ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔrebɔ aboboano pono no mu no, abaawa bi a ne din de Rode ba bɛtiee.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔtee Petro nne no, anigyeɛ nti wammue ɛpono no, na ɔtutuu mmirika kɔkaa sɛ Petro gyina ɛpono no akyi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na wɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Woabɔ dam! Na ɔkɔɔ so ara kaa sɛ ɛte saa. Na wɔkaa sɛ: Ɛyɛ ne bɔfoɔ!",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Petro da so rebɔ pono no mu ara; na wɔbueeɛ no, wɔhunuu no, na wɔn ho dwirii wɔn.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔde ne nsa nyamm wɔn sɛ wɔmmua wɔn ano, na ɔkaa sɛdeɛ Awurade yii no firii afiase hɔ no kyerɛɛ wɔn. Na ɔse: Monkɔka nsɛm yi nkyerɛ Yakobo ne anuanom no. Na ɔfirii hɔ kɔɔ baabi foforɔ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, ahoyera a ɛbaa asraafoɔ no mu nyɛ adewa, sɛ ɛdeɛn ara na ayɛ Petro.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Herode hwehwɛɛ no na wanhu no no, ɔbisaa awɛmfoɔ no sɛ ɛyɛeɛ, na ɔhyɛɛ sɛ wɔnkɔkum wɔn. Na ɔsiane firii Yudea kɔɔ Kaesarea kɔtenaa hɔ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Afei na Herode afa Tirofoɔ ne Sidonfoɔ ho abufuo; enti wɔyɛɛ nokorɔ baa ne nkyɛn, na wɔde bɛbɔɔ ɔhene dabehene Blasto so sɛ ɔnsrɛ amannwoeɛ mma wɔn, ɛfiri sɛ ɔhene no asase so na wɔnya nnuane.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na da a wɔhyɛeɛ duruiɛ no, Herode hyɛɛ n’ahentadeɛ, na ɔtenaa asɛnnie adwa so, na ɔkaa asɛm kyerɛɛ wɔn.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ɔman no huroo sɛ: Onyame bi nne nie, na ɛnyɛ onipa deɛ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na amonom hɔ ara na Awurade bɔfoɔ bɛbɔɔ no, ɛfiri sɛ wamfa animuonyam amma Onyankopɔn; na ɔdɔree mmoaa, na ɔwuiɛ.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na Nyankopɔn asɛm no kɔɔ so, na ɛtrɛe.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na Barnaba ne Saulo wiee wɔn som no, wɔsane firii Yerusalem, na wɔfaa Yohane a wɔfrɛ no Marko nso kaa wɔn ho."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Nso asafo a ɛwɔ Antiokia no, na adiyifoɔ ne akyerɛkyerɛfoɔ bi wɔ mu, wɔne Barnaba ne Simeon a wɔfrɛ no Niger, ne Kireneni Lukio, ne Manaen a wɔtetee no ne Ɔmansinihene Herode, ne Saulo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na wɔresom Awurade na wɔredi mmuada no, Honhom Kronkron kaa sɛ: Monyi Barnaba ne Saulo mma me na wɔnkɔ adwuma a enti mafrɛ wɔn no mu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ɛnna wɔdii mmuada na wɔbɔɔ mpaeɛ na wɔde wɔn nsa guu wɔn soɔ no, wɔgyaa wɔn kwan.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na afei Honhom Kronkron somaa wɔn saa no, wɔsii mu kɔɔ Seleukia, na wɔfiri hɔ nam suhyɛn mu kɔɔ Kipro.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na wɔduruu Salami no, wɔkaa Nyankopɔn asɛm Yudafoɔ hyia adan mu; na Yohane nso ka wɔn ho sɛ ɔsomfoɔ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na wɔtwaa mu supɔ no so kɔduruu Pafo no, wɔhunuu osumanni odiyifoɔ torofoɔ bi a ɔyɛ Yudani a ne din de Bar-Yesu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ɔno na na ɔka Amrado Sergio Paulo a ɔyɛ ɔbadwemma ho. Ɔno na ɔfrɛɛ Barnaba ne Saulo, ɛfiri sɛ na ɔrepɛ Nyankopɔn asɛm atie.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na osumanni Elima no (nso sɛdeɛ ne din nkyerɛaseɛ teɛ ara ne no) sii wɔn kwan, na ɔhwehwɛɛ sɛ ɔdane amrado no firi gyidie no ho.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Saulo a wɔfrɛ no Paulo nso a Honhom Kronkron ahyɛ no ma no hwɛɛ no dinn",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> kaa sɛ: Wo a nnaadaa ne mmusuo nyinaa ayɛ wo ma, ɔbonsam ba, tenenee nyinaa tamfo, worennyae Awurade kwan a ɛtene no konton anaa?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na afei, hwɛ, Awurade nsa da wo so, na w’ani bɛfira, na worenhunu owia, gye da bi. Na amonom hɔ ara kusukuukuu ne esum bɛduruu no so maa no kyini hwehwɛɛ obi a ɔbɛsɔ ne nsa akyerɛ ne kwan.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛberɛ a amrado no hunuu deɛ asie no, ɔgye diiɛ, na Awurade nkyerɛkyerɛ no yɛɛ no ahodwiri.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Paulo ne ne mfɛfoɔ tu firii Pafo no, wɔbaa Perge a ɛwɔ Pamfilia; na Yohane twee ne ho firii wɔn ho sane kɔɔ Yerusalem.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔn deɛ, wɔfirii Perge no, wɔtwaa mu baa Antiokia a ɛwɔ Pisidia, na wɔkɔɔ hyiadan mu homeda kɔtenaa ase.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na wɔwiee mmara ne adiyifoɔ no kenkan no, hyiadan no mu mpanimfoɔ soma baa wɔn nkyɛn sɛ: Anuanom, sɛ mowɔ afotusɛm bi a mobɛka akyerɛ ɔman no a, monka!",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Paulo sɔre gyinae, na ɔde ne nsa nyamm kaa sɛ: Israel mmarima ne mo a mosuro Onyankopɔn, montie!",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Israel man yi, Nyankopɔn na ɔyii yɛn agyanom, na ɔman no te Misraim asase so sɛ ahɔhoɔ no, ɔmaa wɔn so, na ɔde nsa a wama soɔ yii wɔn firii hɔ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɛbɛyɛ mfirinhyia aduanan na ɔkuraa wɔn mu nyaa wɔn ho boasetɔ danedanee wɔn, ɛserɛ so.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔsɛee aman nson Kanaan asase soɔ no, ɔkyɛɛ wɔn asase no maa wɔn.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na ɛno akyiri bɛyɛ mfirinhyia ahanan aduonum no, ɔmaa wɔn atemmufoɔ de bɛsii Odiyifoɔ Samuel so.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɛfiri ɔno soɔ no, wɔbisaa sɛ wɔmma wɔn ɔhene; na Onyankopɔn de Saulo, Kis ba a ɔfiri Benyamin abusuakuo mu maa wɔn mfirinhyia aduanan.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ɔtuu no no, ɔmaa Dawid so de no sii wɔn so hene; ɔno nso na ɔdii no adanseɛ sɛ: Mahunu Dawid, Yisai ba, ɔbarima a m’akoma pɛ no, ɔno na ɔbɛyɛ deɛ mepɛ nyinaa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Oyi asefoɔ mu na Onyankopɔn dii ne bɔhyɛ soɔ yii Yesu yɛɛ no Israel Agyenkwa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Nso Yohane kaa adwensakyera asubɔ kyerɛɛ Israel man no nyinaa ansa na ɔreba.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na Yohane reyɛ awie ne dwumadie no, ɔkaa sɛ: Mosusu sɛ mene hwan? Ɛnyɛ mene no; na hwɛ, obi di m’akyiri reba a mensɛ sɛ mesane ne nan ase mpaboa.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Anuanom, Abraham asefoɔ ne mo mu nnipa a mosuro Onyankopɔn no, yɛn na wɔasoma nkwagyeɛ asɛm yi abrɛ yɛn.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ɛsiane sɛ wɔn a wɔte Yerusalem ne wɔn mpanimfoɔ nnim no ne adiyifoɔ nsɛm a wɔkenkan daa homeda no nti, wɔbuu no fɔ de maa nsɛm no baa mu.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na wɔanhunu adeɛ biara a ɛfata owuo wɔ ne mu, nanso wɔsrɛɛ Pilato sɛ wɔnku no.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na wɔwiee deɛ wɔatwerɛ ne ho nyinaa no, wɔyii no firii dua no ho de no kɔtoo ɛda mu.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na Onyankopɔn nyanee no firii awufoɔ mu,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> na nna bebree, ɔyii ne ho adi kyerɛɛ wɔn a wɔne no firi Galilea baa Yerusalem no; wɔn ara ne n’adansefoɔ ma ɔman no.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na yɛn deɛ, yɛka mo bɔ a wɔhyɛɛ agyanom no ho asɛmpa",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> sɛ Onyankopɔn ama no aba mu koraa ama yɛn a yɛyɛ wɔn mma, na wanyane Yesu, sɛdeɛ wɔatwerɛ no Dwom a ɛtɔ so mmienu no mu sɛ: Wone me ba, ɛnnɛ na mawo woɔ.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na sɛ ɔnyanee no firii awufoɔ mu, na ɔrensane nkɔ porɔ mu bio no, ɔkaa no wɔ saa kwan yi so sɛ: Mede Dawid adonneɛ a ɛsi hɔ pintinn no bɛma mo.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Enti nso ɔkaa no Dwom foforɔ mu sɛ: Woremma wo kronkronni no nhunu porɔeɛ.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na Dawid deɛ, ɔsomm ɔno ara ne berɛ so sɛdeɛ Nyankopɔn pɛ wieeɛ no, ɔwuiɛ, na wɔde no kɔtoo n’agyanom nkyɛn, na ɔhunuu porɔeɛ;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> nanso deɛ Onyankopɔn nyanee no no anhunu porɔeɛ.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Enti, anuanom, monhunu sɛ ɛnam oyi so na wɔka bɔne fakyɛ kyerɛ mo;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> na nnoɔma a montumi nni ho bem Mose mmara mu no nyinaa, oyi mu na obiara a ɔgye die no di ho bem.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Enti monhwɛ yie, na asɛm a wɔaka no adiyifoɔ mu no amma mo so sɛ:",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Monhwɛ, mo fɛdifoɔ, na ɛnyɛ mo nwanwa na monyera; ɛfiri sɛ meyɛ adwuma bi wɔ mo berɛ so, adwuma a sɛ obi ka kyerɛ mo a, morennye nnie.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na wɔfiri hyiadan mu hɔ firii adie no, wɔsrɛɛ sɛ homeda foforɔ wɔmmɛka nsɛm no nkyerɛ wɔn bio.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Na wɔn a wɔahyia mu no paepaee mu no, Yudafoɔ ne wɔn a wɔadane Yudafoɔ nyamesurofoɔ no mu bebree dii Paulo ne Barnaba akyi, na wɔkasa kyerɛɛ wɔn tuu wɔn fo sɛ wɔntena Nyankopɔn adom no mu.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Na homeda foforɔ duruiɛ no, ɛkaa kumaa, na anka kuro mu no nyinaa bɛhyiaa sɛ wɔrebɛtie Nyankopɔn asɛm.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Na Yudafoɔ no hunuu nkurɔfoɔ akuakuo no, anibereɛ nti, wɔkasakasa tiaa deɛ Paulo reka no gyee no akyinnyeɛ, na wɔkaa abususɛm.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Na Paulo ne Barnaba de akokoɔduro kaa sɛ: Ɛhia sɛ anka wɔka Nyankopɔn asɛm no kyerɛ mo kane; na ɛnam sɛ mosum twene na mobu mo ho sɛ monsɛ daa nkwa yi, hwɛ, yɛdane kɔ amanaman no nkyɛn.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Na saa ara na Awurade ahyɛ yɛn sɛ: Mede wo masi hɔ sɛ amanaman kanea, na woayɛ nkwagyeɛ akɔduru asase ano.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Na amanaman mufoɔ no teeɛ no, wɔn ani gyee, na wɔhyɛɛ Awurade asɛm no animuonyam. Na dodoɔ a wɔayi wɔn ama daa nkwa no gye dii.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Na Awurade asɛm no trɛɛ asase no nyinaa so.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Na Yudafoɔ no hwanyann mmaa nyamesurofoɔ a wɔwɔ din ne kuro no mu atitire, na wɔmaa ɔtaa baa Paulo ne Barnaba so, na wɔpamm wɔn firii wɔn asase so.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Ɛnna wɔporoporoo wɔn nan ase mfuturo guu wɔn soɔ, na wɔbaa Ikonium.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Na asuafoɔ no deɛ, anigyeɛ ne Honhom Kronkron hyɛɛ wɔn ma."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ Ikonium nso wɔn baanu no kɔɔ Yudafoɔ hyiadan mu, na wɔkɔkaa asɛm maa Yudafoɔ ne Helafoɔ pii gye diiɛ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Yudafoɔ a wɔnnye nni no hwanyann amanaman mufoɔ no maa wɔnyaa anuanom no ho adwemmɔne.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Enti wɔtenaa hɔ kyɛree, na wɔde nnam paee mu kasa maa Awurade, na ɔno nso dii n’adom asɛm no ho adanseɛ, na ɔnam wɔn nsa so maa wɔyɛɛ nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ ne anwanwadeɛ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Nanso kuro mu hɔfoɔ no mu paee, ɔfa wɔ Yudafoɔ no afa, na ɔfa nso wɔ asomafoɔ no afa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na amanaman mufoɔ no ne Yudafoɔ ne wɔn mpanimfoɔ no bɔɔ kirididi baa sɛ wɔrebɛbɔ wɔn adapaa, na wɔakɔsi wɔn aboɔ no,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> wɔhunui, na wɔdwane kɔɔ Likaonia nkuro Listra ne Derbe ne asase a ɛda ho no so;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> na wɔtenaa hɔ kaa asɛmpa no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔbarima bi wɔ Listra a ɔntumi nnyina ne nan soɔ, na ɔte hɔ, ɔyɛ obubuani firi ne na yam, na ɔnnantee da.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Oyi tee sɛ Paulo rekasa; na Paulo nso hwɛɛ no dinn hunuu sɛ ɔwɔ gyidie sɛ ɔbɛnya ayaresa,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> enti ɔde nne kɛseɛ kaa sɛ: Sɔre gyina wo nan so kyirebenn! Na ɔhurihurii, na ɔnanteeɛ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na nkurɔfoɔ akuakuo no hunuu deɛ Paulo ayɛ no, wɔmaa wɔn nne so kaa no Likaonia kasa mu sɛ: Anyame ayeyɛ wɔn ho sɛ nnipa asianesiane aba yɛn nkyɛn!",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wɔfrɛɛ Barnaba Seus, na Paulo nso, wɔfrɛɛ no Hermes, ɛfiri sɛ ɔno na na ɔka asɛm.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Seus a n’asɔredan wɔ kuro no anim no sɔfoɔ de anantwinini ne nhwiren a wɔakyekyerɛ baa kuro no aboboano pɛɛ sɛ ɔne nkurɔfoɔ akuakuo no de bɛbɔ afɔdeɛ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na asomafoɔ Barnaba ne Paulo teeɛ no, wɔsunsuanee wɔn ntoma mu tutuu mmirika kɔɔ nkurɔfokuo no mu teaa mu sɛ:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Mmarima, adɛn na moreyɛ yeinom? Yɛn nso yɛyɛ nnipa te sɛ mo ara, na yɛka asɛmpa kyerɛ mo sɛ monnane mfiri ahuhudeɛ yi ho nkɔ Onyankopɔn a ɔte ase no nkyɛn; ɔno na ɔyɛɛ ɔsoro ne asase ne ɛpo ne deɛ ɛwɔ mu nyinaa.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɔno na tete berɛ a atwa mu no mu no, ɔmaa amanaman nyinaa kwan sɛ wɔmfa wɔn ara wɔn akwan soɔ;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> nanso wannyae ne ho adansedie, yɛɛ yie maa mo nsuo firi soro ne berɛ a aduane ba, na ɔde aduane ne anigyeɛ maa mo abotɔyam.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na nsɛm a wɔkaeɛ yi nyinaa akyi mpo, wɔbrɛɛ ansa na wɔretumi ama nkurɔfoɔ akuakuo no agyae wɔn afɔdeɛ no bɔ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Yudafoɔ bi firi Antiokia ne Ikonium baa hɔ; na wɔbɛhyɛɛ nkurɔfoɔ akuakuo no kutupa, na wɔsii Paulo aboɔ no, wɔtwee no firii kuro no mu susuu sɛ wawu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na asuafoɔ no bɛtwaa ne ho hyiaeɛ no, ɔsɔre kɔɔ kuro no mu. Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, ɔne Barnaba firii hɔ kɔɔ Derbe.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na wɔkaa asɛmpa no kyerɛɛ kuro mu hɔfoɔ na wɔdanee nnipa bebree asuafoɔ no, wɔsane kɔɔ Listra ne Ikonium ne Antiokia",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> hyehyɛɛ asuafoɔ no akra den, tutuu wɔn fo sɛ wɔntena gyidie mu, kaa nso sɛ ɛtwa sɛ yɛnam amanehunu pii mu kɔ Nyankopɔn ahennie mu.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wɔsisii mpanimfoɔ maa wɔn, asafo biara mu, na wɔde mmuada bɔɔ mpaeɛ no, wɔde wɔn hyɛɛ Awurade a wɔagye no adie no nsa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na wɔtwaa mu wɔ Pisidia no, wɔbaa Pamfilia.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na wɔkaa asɛm no wɔ Perge no, wɔbɛduruu Atalia.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na wɔfirii hɔ faa nsuo ani baa Antiokia, faako a wɔde wɔn hyɛɛ Onyankopɔn adom nsa maa adwuma a wɔakɔwie no.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na wɔbaeɛ na wɔfrɛɛ asafo no boaa ano no, wɔkaa deɛ Onyankopɔn de wɔn akɔyɛ nyinaa ne sɛdeɛ wabue gyidie pono ama amanaman mufoɔ no.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na wɔne asuafoɔ no tenaa hɔ kyɛree."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na nnipa bi firi Yudea ba bɛkyerɛkyerɛɛ anuanom no sɛ: Sɛ wɔantwa mo twetia sɛdeɛ Mose amanneɛ teɛ no a, montumi nnya nkwagyeɛ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na afei akasakasa ne akyinnyegyeɛ denden bi baa Paulo ne Barnaba ɛne wɔn ntam no, wɔhyɛɛ sɛ asɛm no nti Paulo ne Barnaba ne wɔn mu binom nso nkɔ asomafoɔ ne mpanimfoɔ no nkyɛn wɔ Yerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na asafo no gyaa wɔn kwan no, wɔkɔfaa Foinike ne Samaria kaa amanaman no adwensakyera ho asɛm, na wɔmaa anuanom no nyinaa ani gyee kɛseɛ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na wɔduruu Yerusalem no, asafo no ne asomafoɔ ne mpanimfoɔ no gyee wɔn, na wɔkaa deɛ Onyankopɔn de wɔn ayɛ nyinaa kyerɛɛ wɔn.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ebinom a wɔfiri Farisifoɔ fekuo mu a wɔagye adie sɔree, na wɔkaa sɛ ɛsɛ sɛ wɔtwa wɔn twetia na wɔhyɛ wɔn sɛ wɔnni Mose mmara no soɔ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na asomafoɔ ne mpanimfoɔ no bɛhyiaa sɛ wɔbɛhwɛ asɛm yi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na wɔgyee ho akyinnyeɛ pii no, Petro sɔre ka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Anuanom, mo ara monim sɛ mfitiaseɛ no ara na Onyankopɔn yii me wɔ yɛn mu sɛ me na amanaman no mfa m’anomu asɛm so nte asɛmpa no na wɔnnye nni.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Onyankopɔn a ɔnim akoma mu no dii wɔn adanseɛ maa wɔn Honhom Kronkron sɛdeɛ ɔmaa yɛn nso no;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> na wamma no ansono yɛne wɔn, na mmom ɔnam gyidie so tee wɔn akoma mu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Afei adɛn na mosɔ Onyankopɔn hwɛ, sɛ mode kɔnnua a yɛn agyanom ne yɛn antumi ansoa to asuafoɔ no kɔn soɔ?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Awurade Yesu adom so mmom na yɛgye di sɛ wɔnam bɛgye yɛn nkwa, sɛ wɔn nso.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na nnipakuo no nyinaa yɛɛ komm, na wɔtiee Barnaba ne Paulo a wɔreka nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ ne anwanwadeɛ a Onyankopɔn nam wɔn so ayɛ no amanaman no mu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na wɔn ano siiɛ no, Yakobo buaa sɛ: Anuanom, montie me!",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Simeon aka sɛdeɛ kane Onyankopɔn kɔhwɛɛ amanaman no, sɛ ɔreyi wɔn mu nnipa ama ne din.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Yei so na adiyifoɔ no nsɛm sie, sɛdeɛ wɔatwerɛ sɛ:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Yeinom akyiri no mɛsane mabɛsi Dawid ntomadan a ahwe ase no bio, na masi deɛ wɔadwirie no bio, na mama so bio.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na nnipa a aka no ne amanaman a wɔbɛbɔ me din wɔ mu no nyinaa ahwehwɛ Awurade akyiri kwan",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Awurade a ɔma wɔhunuu yeinom nyinaa firi wiase asefire no na ɔka.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Enti m’asɛm a mewɔ meka ne sɛ: Wɔnnha wɔn a wɔfiri amanaman no mu adane aba Nyankopɔn nkyɛn no;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na wɔntwerɛ nkɔma wɔn sɛ: Wɔnyi wɔn ho mfiri abosom afideɛ ne adwamammɔ ne mmoa a wɔanhwie wɔn mogya anguo na wɔwuiɛ ne mogya ho.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɛfiri tete no na Mose wɔ wɔn a wɔka n’asɛm nkuro nyinaa mu, na wɔkenkan no hyia adan mu daa homeda.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Enti ɛyɛɛ asomafoɔ ne mpanimfoɔ ne asafo mu no sɛ ɛyɛ sɛ wɔyi wɔn mu nnipa bi soma wɔn ka Paulo ne Barnaba ho kɔ Antiokia, wɔne Yuda a wɔfrɛ no Barsaba nso, ne Silas, anuanom no mu nnipa atitire,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> na wɔtwerɛɛ nwoma hyɛɛ wɔn nsa sɛ: Asomafoɔ ne anuanom mpanimfoɔ no kyea anuanom a wɔfiri amanaman mu a wɔwɔ Antiokia ne Siria ne Kilikia no.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ɛsiane sɛ yɛate sɛ nnipa bi firi yɛn mu de nsɛm bi abɛtane mo ani, aha mo adwene, nanso yɛanhyɛ wɔn saa nti,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> yɛde nokorɔ hyiaeɛ no, ɛyɛɛ yɛn sɛ ɛyɛ sɛ yɛyi nnipa bi soma wɔn ka yɛn adɔfo Barnaba ne Paulo,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> nnipa a yɛn Awurade Yesu Kristo din nti wɔde wɔn kra ama no, ho ba mo nkyɛn.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Enti yɛasoma Yuda ne Silas a wɔde ano nso bɛka nsɛm no ara.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na ɛsɔɔ Honhom Kronkron ne yɛn ani sɛ, wɔmfa adesoa bi nto mo soɔ, gye deɛ ɛhia yi ara, ɛne",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> sɛ monyi mo ho mfiri nam a wɔakum ama abosom ne mogya ne mmoa a wɔanhwie wɔn mogya anguo na wɔwuiɛ ne adwamammɔ mu; ɛno na sɛ moyi mo ho firi ho a, ɛyɛ. Ɛnsi mo yie!",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na afei wɔgyaa wɔn kwan no, wɔbaa Antiokia; na wɔmaa asafo no hyiaeɛ no, wɔyii nwoma no mae.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na wɔkenkaneeɛ no, awerɛkyekyerɛ no nti wɔn ani gyee.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na Yuda ne Silas a wɔn nso yɛ adiyifoɔ no de nsɛm pii tuu anuanom no fo, na wɔhyɛɛ wɔn den.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na wɔkyɛree hɔ kakra no, anuanom no gyaa wɔn kwan dwoodwoo kɔɔ wɔn a wɔsomaa wɔn no nkyɛn.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> [Nanso ɛyɛɛ Silas sɛ ɔntena hɔ ara.]",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na Paulo ne Barnaba ne nnipa pii a wɔka wɔn ho nso tenaa Antiokia kyerɛkyerɛe, na wɔkaa Awurade asɛmpa no.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na nna bi twaa mu no, Paulo ka kyerɛɛ Barnaba sɛ: Ma yɛnsane nkɔhwɛ anuanom no nkuro a yɛaka Awurade asɛm no hɔ nyinaa mu, nkɔhwɛ sɛdeɛ wɔteɛ.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na Barnaba kaa sɛ wɔbɛfa Yohane a wɔfrɛ no Marko aka wɔn ho.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Nanso Paulo susuu sɛ ɛnyɛ sɛ wɔbɛfa deɛ ɔtwee ne ho firii wɔn ho Pamfilia na ɔne wɔn ankɔyɛ adwuma no aka wɔn ho.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Ɛnna akasakasa a emu yɛ den baeɛ, na ɛmaa wɔpaepaee mu, na Barnaba faa Marko faa nsuo ani kɔɔ Kipro;",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> na Paulo faa Silas, na anuanom no de no hyɛɛ Nyankopɔn adom nsa no, ɔsii mu kɔe.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Na ɔkɔtwaa mu Siria ne Kilikia hyɛɛ asafo no den."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Paulo kɔduruu Derbe ne Listra nso, baabi a na osuani bi wɔ hɔ a ne din de Timoteo a ɔyɛ Yudani baa bi a ɔyɛ gyidini ba, nanso n’agya yɛ Helani.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na anuanom a wɔwɔ Listra ne Ikonium no bɔ no din pa.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ɔno na Paulo pɛɛ sɛ ɔne no korɔ, na Yudafoɔ a wɔwɔ fa mu hɔ no nti, ɔfaa no twaa no twetia, ɛfiri sɛ na wɔn nyinaa nim sɛ n’agya yɛ Helani.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na wɔretwa mu nkuro no mu no, wɔde mmara a asomafoɔ ne mpanimfoɔ a wɔwɔ Yerusalem no hyɛɛ sɛ wɔnni soɔ no maa wɔn.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɛnna asafo ahodoɔ no yɛɛ den gyidie mu, na wɔkɔɔ so dɔree daa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na wɔtwaa mu Frigia ne Galatia asase so, ɛfiri sɛ Honhom Kronkron sii wɔn kwan sɛ wɔnnka asɛm no Asia.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na wɔduruu Misia ntentensoɔ no, wɔpɛɛ sɛ anka wɔkɔ Bitinia, nanso Yesu honhom no amma wɔn kwan.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Enti wɔsianee Misia ho baa Troa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na anadwo no, Paulo hunuu anisoadeɛ sɛ ɔbarima bi a ɔfiri Makedonia gyina hɔ resrɛ no sɛ: Twa mu bra Makedonia bɛboa yɛn!",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɔhunuu anisoadeɛ no ara pɛ na yɛpɛɛ sɛ yɛkɔ Makedonia, ɛfiri sɛ ɛyɛɛ yɛn sɛ Onyankopɔn na afrɛ yɛn ampa sɛ yɛnkɔka asɛmpa no nkyerɛ wɔn.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɛnna yɛsii suhyɛn mu tu firii Troa de mmirika tene baa Samotrake. Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, yɛbaa Neapoli.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na yɛfirii hɔ kɔɔ Filipi a ɛyɛ Makedonia mansini kuropɔn mu. Na yɛdii kuro yi mu nna kakra.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na homeda duruiɛ no, yɛfirii kuro no mu kɔɔ asuo bi ho baabi a yɛsusuu sɛ wɔbɔ mpaeɛ hɔ. Na yɛtenaa aseɛ no, yɛkasa kyerɛɛ mmaa a wɔabɛhyia hɔ no.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔbaa bi a ne din de Lidia a ɔtɔn ntoma kɔkɔɔ a ɔfiri Tiatira kuro mu, a ɔsom Onyankopɔn tiee; na Awurade buee n’akomam sɛ ɔntie deɛ Paulo reka no.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na wɔbɔɔ ɔno ne ne fiefoɔ asu no, ɔsrɛɛ sɛ: Sɛ moabu me sɛ megye Awurade medi nokorɛ mu a, mommra mmɛtena me fie; na ɔsrɛɛ yɛn ara maa yɛn ne no kɔe.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ yɛrekɔ bɔ mpaeɛ no, abaawa bi a ɔwɔ akɔm honhom bɛhyiaa yɛn; nso na ɔde nkɔmhyɛ ama ne wuranom anya wɔn ho sɛ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɔno na ɔdii Paulo ne yɛn akyiri teaa mu sɛ: Nnipa yi ne Onyankopɔn a ɔwɔ sorosoro no nkoa a wɔkyerɛ mo nkwagyeɛ kwan.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ yei nna bebree. Na ɛyɛɛ Paulo ahomete, na ɔdanee ne ho ka kyerɛɛ honhom no sɛ: Mehyɛ wo Yesu Kristo din mu sɛ: Firi adi firi ne mu! Na dɔn no ara mu ɔfirii adi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ne wuranom hunuu sɛ wɔn mfasoɔ abɔ wɔn no, wɔsɔɔ Paulo ne Silas mu twee wɔn kɔɔ edwa mu mpanimfoɔ anim,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na wɔde wɔn kɔmaa asafohene sɛ: Nnipa yi yɛ Yudafoɔ a wɔretane yɛn kuro yi ani,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> na wɔkyerɛ amanneɛ bi a yɛnni ho kwan sɛ yɛgyeɛ anaasɛ yɛyɛ, ɛfiri sɛ yɛyɛ Romafoɔ.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na nkurɔfokuo no nso sɔre tiaa wɔn, na asafohene no yii wɔn ho ntadeɛ hyɛɛ sɛ wɔmmɔ wɔn mmaa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wɔkaa wɔn mmaa pii no, wɔde wɔn kɔguu afiase hyɛɛ ofiasehwɛfoɔ no nsa sɛ ɔmfa wɔn nsie yie.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ɔno nso, wɔhyɛɛ no saa no, ɔde wɔn kɔguu afiase a ɛwɔ mfimfini no mu, na ɔde wɔn nan bobɔɔ dua mu.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na dasuo mu no, Paulo ne Silas bɔɔ mpaeɛ too dwom maa Onyankopɔn; na nneduafoɔ no tieeɛ.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na mpofirim ara asasewosoɔ kɛseɛ maa afiase no nnyinasoɔ wosoe, na amonom hɔ ara apono no nyinaa buebuee, na wɔn nyinaa ahoma sanesanee.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ofiasehwɛfoɔ no firi nna mu nyaneeɛ na ɔhunuu sɛ afiase apono no abuebue no, ɔtwee ne nkrantɛ sɛ anka ɔrebɛdi ne ho awu, ɛfiri sɛ ɔsusuu sɛ nneduafoɔ no adwane.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na Paulo de nne kɛseɛ teaa mu sɛ: Nyɛ wo ho bɔne bi, na yɛn nyinaa wɔ ha.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na ɔbisaa kanea de mmirika bae, na ɔde ahopopoɔ bɛhwɛɛ Paulo ne Silas anim,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> na ɔde wɔn firii adie no, ɔkaa sɛ: Awuranom, menyɛ dɛn na wɔagye me nkwa?",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na wɔse: Gye Awurade Yesu di, na wɔbɛgye wo ne wo fiefoɔ nkwa.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na wɔkaa Awurade asɛm kyerɛɛ ɔno ne wɔn a wɔwɔ ne fie nyinaa.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na ɔfaa wɔn anadwo dɔn no ara mu hohoroo wɔn akuro no, na ɔmaa wɔbɔɔ ɔne wɔn a wɔyɛ ne fiefoɔ nyinaa asu amonom hɔ ara.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na ɔde wɔn baa ne fie too wɔn pono, na sɛ wɔagye Onyankopɔn adie nti, ɔne ne fiefoɔ nyinaa ho sanee wɔn.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, asafohene no somaa asraafoɔ baa sɛ: Gyaa nnipa no na wɔnkɔ.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na ofiasehwɛfoɔ no kaa nsɛm yi kyerɛɛ Paulo sɛ: Asafohene no asoma sɛ wɔnnyaa mo mma monkɔ; enti afei momfiri adi nkɔ dwoodwoo.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ɛnna Paulo ka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Wɔammu yɛn atɛn, na wɔahwe yɛn a yɛyɛ Romafoɔ edwa mu, na wɔde yɛn agu afiase, afei ansa na wɔpɛ sɛ wopamo yɛn kodɛɛ anaa? Dabi da, na ma wɔn ara wɔmmɛyi yɛn.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Na asraafoɔ no kɔkaa nsɛm yi kyerɛɛ asafohene no; na wɔtee sɛ wɔyɛ Romafoɔ no, wɔsuroeɛ.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na wɔba bɛpaa wɔn kyɛw maa wɔn dibem, na wɔyii wɔn srɛɛ wɔn sɛ wɔmfiri kuro no mu nkɔ.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na wɔfirii afiase hɔ kɔɔ Lidia fie. Na wɔhunuu anuanom no, wɔkyekyeree wɔn werɛ, na wɔfiri hɔ kɔeɛ."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na wɔtwaa mu wɔ Amfipoli ne Apolonia baa Tesalonika; ɛhɔ na Yudafoɔ hyiadan wɔ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na sɛdeɛ Paulo taa yɛ no, ɔkɔɔ wɔn nkyɛn homeda mmiɛnsa ne wɔn kɔyɛɛ twerɛ nsɛm ho mpɛnsɛnpɛnsɛm.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ɔkyerɛkyerɛɛ mu dii ho adanseɛ sɛ ɛtwa sɛ Kristo no hunu amane, na ɔsɔre firi awufoɔ mu. Na ɔse: Yesu a meka mo ne ho asɛm yi ara ne Kristo no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na wɔn mu binom gye dii, na wɔde wɔn ho bɔɔ Paulo ne Silas ho, wɔne Helafoɔ nyamesurofoɔ no mu pii ne mmaa mpanimfoɔ no mu fa kɛseɛ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Yudafoɔ no ani bereeɛ, na wɔfaa ahuhufoɔ no mu nnipa bɔne bi kaa wɔn ho, na wɔmaa nkurɔfoɔ no bɔɔ bum bɛhyiae, na wɔdanee kuro no ani butui, na wɔkɔtwaa Yason dan ho hyiaeɛ, hwehwɛɛ sɛ wɔyi wɔn firi adi de wɔn kɔma nkurɔfoɔ no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na wɔanhu wɔn no, wɔtwee Yason ne anuanom no bi kɔmaa kuro no mu mpanimfoɔ, na wɔteateaa mu sɛ: Yeinom a wɔadane wiase ani abutuo no aba ha nso!",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Yason agye wɔn. Nso wɔn nyinaa bu Kaesare mmara no so ka sɛ, ɔhene foforɔ bi wɔ hɔ a wɔfrɛ no Yesu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na nkurɔfoɔ no ne ɔman mpanimfoɔ no tee yei no, ɛhaa wɔn pa ara.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Yason ne wɔn a aka no dii agyinamu maa wɔn no, wɔgyaa wɔn ma wɔkɔe.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ntɛm ara anuanom no gyaa Paulo ne Silas kwan anadwo kɔɔ Beroia; na wɔduruu hɔ no, wɔkɔɔ Yudafoɔ hyiadan mu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Yudafoɔ a ɛwɔ ha no yɛ animdefoɔ sene wɔn a wɔwɔ Tesalonika no, ɛfiri sɛ wɔyii wɔn yam pefee gyee asɛm no, na daa na wɔhwehwɛ twerɛsɛm no mu sɛ nnoɔma no te saa anaa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Enti wɔn mu bebree gye dii, wɔne Helafoɔ mmaa a wɔwɔ din ne mmarima no mu fa kɛseɛ ara.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Yudafoɔ a wɔfiri Tesalonika no tee sɛ Paulo akɔka Nyankopɔn asɛm Beroia nso no, wɔbaa hɔ bɛhwanyanee ɛhɔfoɔ no nso.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Enti ntɛm ara na anuanom no gyaa Paulo kwan sɛ ɔnkɔ mpoano; na Silas ne Timoteo deɛ, wɔtenaa hɔ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na wɔn a wɔkɔgyaa Paulo no de no kɔɔ Atene. Ɔkraa wɔn sɛ Silas ne Timoteo mmra ne nkyɛn ntɛmntɛm no, wɔsii mu kɔe.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Paulo retwɛn wɔn wɔ Atene na ɔhunuu sɛ kuro no de wɔn ho ama abosonsom no, ɛyɛɛ no ahometeɛ pa ara.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Enti hyiadan mu, na ɔne Yudafoɔ ne nyamesurofoɔ no yɛɛ nhwehwɛmu dendeenden, na edwa mu nso, daa na ɔne wɔn a ɔbɛto wɔn no dii anobaebaeɛ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Epikurofoɔ ne Stoafoɔ anyansapɛfoɔ bi nso ne no di anobaebaeɛ. Ebinom kaa sɛ: Ɔpɔtɔni yi se deɛn nie? Na ebinom se: Wayɛ sɛdeɛ ɔka abosom ahɔhoɔ bi ho asɛm. (Na ɔreka wɔn Yesu ne owusɔreɛ ho asɛmpa no.)",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ɛnna wɔfaa no de no kɔɔ Areopago kaa sɛ: Wobɛtumi akyerɛ yɛn nkyerɛkyerɛ foforɔ yi ase?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ nsɛm a wode aba yi yɛ yɛn aso mu asɛm foforɔ. Enti yɛpɛ sɛ yɛhunu deɛ ɛkyerɛ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Nso Atenefoɔ ne ahɔhoɔ a wɔabɛtena hɔ nyinaa nni hwee yɛ sɛ wɔbɛka anaa wɔbɛte asɛm foforɔ bie.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Paulo gyinaa Areopago mfimfini kaa sɛ: Atene mmarima, mahunu sɛ mowɔ gyidie wɔ nnoɔma pii mu dodo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ meretwa mu na mehwɛɛ nnoɔma a mosom no, mehunuu afɔrebukyia bi nso a wɔatwerɛ so sɛ: Onyame a wɔnni no dea. Enti deɛ monnim na mosɔre no no, ɔno na meka ne ho asɛm mekyerɛ mo yi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Onyankopɔn a ɔyɛɛ wiase ne deɛ ɛwɔ mu nyinaa, ɔno ara a ɔyɛ ɔsoro ne asase wura no, ɔnte asɔredan a wɔde nsa ayɛ mu,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> nanso wɔmfa nnipa nsa nsom no sɛ deɛ ɛhia no biribie. Ɔno na ɔma nnipa nyinaa nkwa ne ahome ne ade nyinaa;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> na ɔmaa nnipa wɔ aman nyinaa firi onipa baako mu tenaa asase so nyinaa, na wahyehyɛ mmerɛ ahodoɔ ne wɔn tenabea hyeɛ ato hɔ ama wɔn",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> sɛ wɔnhwehwɛ Awurade sɛ ebia wɔbɛte ne nka na wɔahu no, nso ɔne yɛn mu biara ntam kwan nware.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na ɔno mu na yɛte ase, na yɛkeka yɛn ho, na yɛwɔ hɔ, sɛdeɛ mo nnwontofoɔ binom nso aka sɛ: Ɛfiri sɛ n’abusua nso ne yɛn.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na ɛnam sɛ yɛyɛ Nyankopɔn abusua nti, ɛnsɛ sɛ yɛsusu sɛ Nyankopɔn tebea te sɛ sika anaa dwetɛ anaa ɔboɔ, adwini a onipa de ne nyansa ne n’adwene adie.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ne saa nti Onyankopɔn abu n’ani agu mmerɛ ahodoɔ a wɔnnim no so, na afei deɛ, ɔhyɛ nnipa a ɛwɔ mmaa nyinaa sɛ wɔnsakyera wɔn adwene,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> ɛfiri sɛ wayi da bi ato hɔ a ɔnam ɔbarima bi a wayi no asi hɔ so bɛbu wiase atɛn tenenee mu; ɔno na wama no asɔre afiri awufoɔ mu de adi adanseɛ sɛ nnipa nyinaa nnye nni.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na wɔtee awufoɔ sɔreɛ no, ebinom dii fɛw, na ebinom kaa sɛ: Yɛbɛtie wo wɔ asɛm yi ho bio.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Enti Paulo firii wɔn nkyɛn kɔeɛ.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Nso nnipa bi de wɔn ho bɔɔ ne ho, na wɔgye diiɛ; wɔn mu bi ne Dionisio a ɔka Areopago kuo ho ne ɔbaa bi a ne din de Damari ne ebinom a wɔka wɔn ho."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Yeinom akyiri no, Paulo firii Atene kɔɔ Korinto.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔhunuu Yudani bi a ne din de Akwila a wɔwoo no Ponto, na ɔfiri Italia baa hɔ nkyɛreeɛ, ne ne yere Priskila, ɛfiri sɛ Klaudio ahyɛ sɛ Yudafoɔ nyinaa mfiri Roma nkɔ. Paulo kɔɔ wɔn nkyɛn,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na ɛnam sɛ ɔne wɔn yɛ adwuma baako nti, ɔtenaa wɔn nkyɛn yɛɛ adwuma; ɛfiri sɛ wɔyɛ ntomadanyɛfoɔ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na daa homeda ɔkɔka asɛm hyiadan mu maa Yudafoɔ ne Helafoɔ gye diiɛ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na Silas ne Timoteo firi Makedonia baeɛ no, Paulo de nnam kaa asɛm no na ɔdii adanseɛ kyerɛɛ Yudafoɔ sɛ Yesu ne Kristo no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na wɔtuaa ano na wɔkaa abususɛm no, ɔporoo n’atadeɛ mu ka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Mo mogya ngu mo ara mo atifi; me deɛ, me ho afi. Ɛfiri nnɛ merekɔ amanaman no mu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ɛnna ɔfirii hɔ kɔɔ obi a ne din de Tito Yusto a ɔyɛ onyamesuroni, a ne fie bata hyiadan ho no nkyɛn.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na hyiadan mu panin Krispo ne ne fiefoɔ nyinaa gyee Awurade diiɛ, na Korintofoɔ mu bebree a wɔteeɛ no nso gye dii maa wɔbɔɔ wɔn asu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Awurade ka kyerɛɛ Paulo anisoadehunu mu anadwo sɛ: Nsuro, kasa, na mmua w’ano!",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ meka wo ho, na obiara renka wo mmɛyɛ wo hwee; na mewɔ nkurɔfoɔ pii kuro yi mu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔtenaa hɔ afe ne abosome nsia kyerɛkyerɛɛ Nyankopɔn asɛm wɔ wɔn mu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Galio di Akaia amrado no, Yudafoɔ no de anokorɔ sɔre tiaa Paulo, na wɔde no kɔɔ asɛnnie adwa anim",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> kaa sɛ: Oyi tu nnipa aso sɛ wɔnkwati mmara no nsom Onyankopɔn.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na Paulo yɛɛ sɛ ɔrebɛbue n’ano no, Galio ka kyerɛɛ Yudafoɔ no sɛ: Yudafoɔ, sɛ ɛyɛ adeɛ a ɛntene anaa abususɛm bi a, anka ɛsɛ sɛ metie mo;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na sɛ ɛyɛ asɛm ne din ne mo mmara ho asɛmmisa bi deɛ a, ɛnneɛ mo ara monhwɛ! Na me deɛ, merenyɛ saa nsɛm yi temmufoɔ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔpamoo wɔn firii asɛnniiɛ hɔ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Helafoɔ no nyinaa faa hyiadan mu panin Sostene hwee no asɛnniiɛ hɔ, nanso Galio ammu yeinom biara.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na Paulo kɔɔ so tenaa hɔ kyɛree kakra ara yie no, ɔkraa anuanom no, ɔfirii hɔ faa nsuo ani kɔɔ Siria a Priskila ne Akwila ka ne ho; na ɔyii ne ti wɔ Kenkrea; ɛfiri sɛ na wadi nseɛ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na wɔbaa Efeso, na ɔgyaa wɔn hɔ; na ɔno ara deɛ, ɔkɔɔ hyiadan mu ne Yudafoɔ kɔyɛɛ nhwehwɛmu dendeenden.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na wɔsrɛɛ no sɛ ɔntena wɔn nkyɛn nkyɛre kakra no, wampene.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔkraa wɔn sɛ: Sɛ Onyankopɔn pɛ a, mɛsane maba mo nkyɛn bio. Na ɔfirii Efeso sii nsuo ani.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ɔsii fam wɔ Kaesarea no, ɔkɔɔ Yerusalem kɔkyeaa asafo no, na ɔsane kɔɔ Antiokia.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ɔkyɛree hɔ kakra no, ɔfirii hɔ kɔkyinii Galatia ne Frigia nkuro nyinaa mu hyɛɛ asuafoɔ no nyinaa den.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na Yudani bi a ne din de Apolo, a wɔwoo no Aleksandria, onipa a n’ano ateɛ na ɔyɛ nam wɔ twerɛsɛm no mu, baa Efeso.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Oyi na wɔakyerɛkyerɛ no Awurade kwan soɔ; na ɔyɛ hye honhom mu nti, ɔkasae, na ɔkyerɛkyerɛɛ Yesu ho nsɛm yie, nso Yohane asubɔ nkutoo na na ɔnim.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ɔfirii aseɛ de akokoɔduro kasaa hyiadan mu. Na Priskila ne Akwila teeɛ no, wɔfaa no baa wɔn nkyɛn, na wɔkyerɛɛ no Nyankopɔn kwan pɛpɛɛpɛ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ɔpɛɛ sɛ ɔbɛsene akɔ Akaia no, anuanom no hyɛɛ no den, na wɔtwerɛɛ nwoma kɔsrɛɛ asuafoɔ no sɛ wɔnnye no. Na ɔduruu hɔ no, ɔboaa wɔn a wɔnam adom so agye adie no pii.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na ɔde n’asɛm kaa Yudafoɔ no gui wɔ badwam, nam twerɛsɛm so kyerɛɛ pefee sɛ Yesu ne Kristo no."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ berɛ a Apolo wɔ Korinto no, Paulo kyinii amantifi asase so, na ɔbɛduruu Efeso; na ɔbɛtoo asuafoɔ bi no,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ɔbisaa wɔn sɛ: Mogye diiɛ no, monyaa Honhom Kronkron anaa? Na wɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Yɛntee pɛn mpo sɛ Honhom Kronkron bi wɔ baabi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔbisaa wɔn sɛ: Ɛdeɛn mu na wɔbɔɔ mo asu hyɛeɛ? Na wɔse: Yohane asubɔ mu.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Paulo se: Yohane bɔɔ adwensakyera asu mmom, ka kyerɛɛ ɔman no sɛ, wɔnnye deɛ ɔdi n’akyiri reba a ɔne Yesu no nni.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na wɔteeɛ no, wɔmaa wɔbɔɔ wɔn asu hyɛɛ Awurade Yesu din mu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Paulo de ne nsa guu wɔn soɔ no, Honhom Kronkron baa wɔn so, na wɔkaa kasa ahodoɔ pii, na wɔhyɛɛ nkɔm.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na wɔn nyinaa bɛyɛ mmarima dummienu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔkɔɔ hyiadan mu de akokoɔduro kaa asɛm abosome mmiɛnsa, kyerɛkyerɛɛ mu yie ama wɔagye Nyankopɔn ahennie ho asɛm no adi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Nanso na ebinom akoma yɛ den, na wɔntie, na wɔkasa Ɔkwan no ho bɔne nnipakuo no anim nti, ɔgyaa wɔn hɔ yii asuafoɔ no firii wɔn mu, na ɔkasaa wɔ obi a ɔde Tirano suadan mu daa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na saa adeɛ yi kɔɔ so mfeɛ mmienu, na ɛmaa wɔn a wɔte Asia nyinaa, Yudafoɔ ne Helafoɔ, tee Awurade asɛm.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na Onyankopɔn nam Paulo nsa so yɛɛ ahoɔdenneɛ a wɔnka,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> na ɛmaa wɔde ne ho nnuku anaa nsɛnanimu mpo bɛguu ayarefoɔ so, na nyarewa no firii wɔn so, na ahonhommɔne firii wɔn mu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ɛnna Yudafoɔ bi a wɔnam kyini tutu ahonhommɔne no mu binom sii wɔn bo sɛ wɔbɛbɔ Awurade Yesu din wɔ wɔn a wɔwɔ ahonhommɔne so sɛ: Meka Yesu a Paulo ka ne ho asɛm no gu mo so.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Yudani sɔfo panin Skewa mma baason bi na wɔyɛɛ saa.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na honhommɔne no buaa sɛ: Menim Yesu, na menim Paulo, na mone hwannom?",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na onipa a honhommɔne no wɔ ne mu no to hyɛɛ wɔn so yɛɛ wɔn pasaa, na wɔde adagya ne pira dwane firii efie no mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Yudafoɔ ne Helafoɔ a wɔte Efeso nyinaa teeɛ no, ehu kaa wɔn nyinaa, na wɔyii Awurade Yesu din ayɛ kɛse.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na wɔn a wɔagye adie no mu pii ba bɛkaa wɔn bɔne ne wɔn nkokoam nsɛm.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na wɔn a na wɔyɛ asumanneɛ no mu bebree de wɔn nwoma ba bɛhyee no wɔ nnipa nyinaa anim; na wɔbuu ne boɔ ano hunuu sɛ ɛsi nnwetɛbena ɔpeduonum.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Sɛdeɛ Awurade asɛm nam ahoɔden so nyiniiɛ na ɛyɛɛ den ne no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na wɔwiee yeinom no, Paulo bɔɔ ne tiri mu sɛ ɔbɛfa Makedonia ne Akaia akɔ Yerusalem, na ɔse: Meduru hɔ a, akyire yi ɛtwa sɛ mekɔhunu Roma nso.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ɔmaa wɔn a wɔsom no no mu baanu, Timoteo ne Erasto kɔɔ Makedonia, na ɔno ara deɛ ɔkyɛree wɔ Asia kakra.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ɛberɛ no ara mu sakasaka a ɛbaa Ɔkwan no ho nyɛ adewa.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ɛne sɛ, dwetɛdwumfoɔ bi a ne din de Demetrio a ɔde dwetɛ yɛ Artemi asɔredan nsɛsoɔ ma adwumfoɔ nya mfasoɔ kɛseɛ",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> boaa wɔne wɔn a wɔyɛ adwuma yi bie no ano kaa sɛ: Awuranom, monim sɛ adwinnie yi mu na yɛnya yɛn ho.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na mohunu, na mote aseɛ sɛ, ɛnyɛ Efeso ha nko, na ɛrekame ayɛ Asia nyinaa, na Paulo yi atu nkurɔfoɔ bebree aso, adane wɔn ani, ka sɛ: Anyame a wɔde nsa ayɛ nyɛ anyame.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ɛnyɛ yɛn adwuma nko na ɛrekame asɛeɛ, na mmom ɔbosombaa kɛseɛ Artemi asɔrefie rekɔyɛ sɛ wɔmmu no hwee bio, na n’animuonyam kɛseɛ a Asia nyinaa ne wiase de sɔre no no rebɔ no.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na wɔteeɛ no, wɔn bo fui pa ara, na wɔteateaa mu sɛ: Efesofoɔ Artemi yɛ ɔkɛseɛ!",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na basabasa hyɛɛ kuro no ma, na wɔde adwenkorɔ bɔɔ kirididi kɔɔ ahwɛeɛ kɔkyeree Makedoniafoɔ Gaio ne Aristarko a wɔne Paulo nam no.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Paulo pɛɛ sɛ anka ɔkɔhyɛne nkurɔfokuo no mu, nanso asuafoɔ no amma no kwan.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na Asia mpanimfoɔ bi nso a wɔyɛ ne nnamfo soma maa wɔkɔɔ ne nkyɛn kɔsrɛɛ no sɛ ɔnnkɔ ahwɛeɛ hɔ.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na afei ebinom retea mu sɛɛ, na afoforɔ retea mu sɛɛ, ɛfiri sɛ na badwa no mu ayɛ sakasaka, na na ɔfa kɛseɛ no ara nnim adekodeɛ a enti wɔbɛhyiaeɛ.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Afei nnipa bi pempemm Aleksandro sɛ ɔnkasa, ɛfiri sɛ ɔno na Yudafoɔ no de no adi wɔn anim. Na Aleksandro nyamm nkurɔfokuo no pɛɛ sɛ anka oyi n’ano kyerɛ nkurɔfoɔ no.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Nanso wɔhunuu sɛ ɔyɛ Yudani no, wɔn nyinaa de nne korɔ teaa mu bɛyɛ nnɔnhwereɛ mmienu sɛ: Efesofoɔ Artemi yɛ ɔkɛseɛ!",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na ɔtwerɛfoɔ no pataa nkurɔfokuo no sɛ: Efesofoɔ, onipa bɛn mpo na ɔnnim sɛ Efesofoɔ kuro yɛ Artemi kɛseɛ asɔrefie ne ohoni a ɛfiri Seus bɛduruiɛ so hwɛfoɔ?",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na obiara nnye yei ho akyinnyeɛ nti, ɛsɛ sɛ moyɛ komm, na mommfa abufuo nnyɛ biribiara.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Nnipa a mode wɔn aba ha yi nguu asɔrefie ho fi, na wɔnkaa yɛn bosombaa ho abususɛm.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Enti sɛ Demetrio ne adwumfoɔ a wɔka ne ho no wɔ obi ho asɛm bi a, asɛnniiɛ ne amradofoɔ wɔ hɔ; momma wɔmmɛbɔ nkuro.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na sɛ morehwehwɛ nsɛm foforɔ ho biribi a, wɔbɛdi no badwa a wɔhyia mu daa sɛdeɛ mmara no teɛ.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na anhwɛ a, yɛbɛnya nnɛ sakasaka yi ho amane, ɛfiri sɛ wɔkɔtoto yɛn ano mansotwe ho a, yɛnni asɛm biara a yɛde bɛtumi akyerɛ gyegyeegye yi aseɛ.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Na ɔkaa saa no, ɔmaa edwa no tui."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na gyegyeegye no gyaeeɛ no, Paulo frɛɛ asuafoɔ no baa ne nkyɛn, na ɔtuu wɔn fo kraa wɔn firii hɔ sɛ, ɔrekɔ Makedonia.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔtwaa mu hɔnom de nsɛm pii tuu wɔn fo, na ɔbaa Hela.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔdii hɔ abosome mmiɛnsa; na ɔreyɛ atu akɔ Siria no, na Yudafoɔ retɛ no nti, ɔpatu sane bɛfaa Makedonia.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Beroiani Sopater, Piro ba, ne Tesalonikafoɔ Aristarko ne Sekundo ne Derbeni Gaio ne Timoteo ne Asiafoɔ Tihiko ne Trofimo ka ne ho.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Yeinom dii kan kɔtwɛnee yɛn wɔ Troa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na yɛn nso, Apiti nna twaa mu no, yɛfirii Filipi faa nsuo ani, na yɛde nnanum bɛduruu wɔn nkyɛn Troa; ɛhɔ na yɛdii nnanson.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na nnawɔtwe mu da a ɛdi kan no a yɛhyiaa sɛ yɛrebubu paanoo no, Paulo kasa kyerɛɛ wɔn, ɛfiri sɛ adeɛ kye a, ɔbɛkɔ, na ɔtoaa asɛm no so ara kɔsii ɔdasuo mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na nkanea bebree wɔ abansoro faako a yɛahyia mu hɔ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na aberanteɛ bi a ne din de Eutiko te mpomma ano ada hatee, na ɛsiane sɛ Paulo kasa kyɛreeɛ nti, ɔtɔɔ nko firii aborɔsansa no so hwee ase, na wɔmaa no soɔ no, na wawu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Paulo siane kɔbutuu ne so, na ɔyɛɛ no atuu kaa sɛ: Monnha mo ho, na nkwa da so ara wɔ ne mu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔforo bae, na ɔbubuu paanoo, na ɔdiiɛ no, ɔtoaa so kasae ara kɔsii adekyeeɛ, na ɔfirii hɔ kɔeɛ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wɔde abɔfra no baa wɔ anikan so, na ɛyɛɛ wɔn awerɛkyekyerɛ kɛseɛ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na yɛdii kan kɔɔ suhyɛn mu faa nsuo ani kɔɔ Aso sɛ yɛrekɔfa Paulo wɔ hɔ; sɛdeɛ ɔhyehyɛeɛ ne no, ɛfiri sɛ ɔkaa sɛ ɔbɛfa fam akɔ hɔ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔne yɛn hyiaa Aso no, yɛfaa no, na yɛbaa Mitilene.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na yɛtu firii hɔ, na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, yɛbɛduruu Kio ntentensoɔ; na adeɛ kyee bio no, yɛbɛduruu Samo; na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, yɛduruu Mileto.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Paulo aka sɛ ɔbɛsiane Efeso ho, na wankɔkyɛre Asia; ɛfiri sɛ na ɔrepɛ ntɛm, na sɛ ɔbɛtumi a, wakɔduru Yerusalem Pentekoste da.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔfiri Mileto soma kɔɔ Efeso kɔhyiaa asafo no mu mpanimfoɔ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na wɔbaa ne nkyɛn no, ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Monim sɛdeɛ ɛfiri da a ɛdi kan a mebaa Asia no, me ne mo tenaa berɛ no nyinaa mu,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na mede ahobrɛaseɛ adwene nyinaa ne nisuo pii, sɔhwɛ a ɛbaa me soɔ Yudafoɔ pɔ bɔne a wɔbɔɔ no me ho mu mesom Awurade.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na mansi deɛ ɛyɛ mfasoɔ mu biara so, sɛ ebia merenka menkyerɛ mo, na mekyerɛkyerɛɛ mo edwam ne afie mu,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> na medii Nyankopɔn fam adwensakyera ne Awurade Yesu Kristo mu gyidie ho adanseɛ mekyerɛɛ Yudafoɔ ne Helafoɔ.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na afei, hwɛ, Honhom no hyɛ me nti, merekɔ Yerusalem, na mennim deɛ ɛbɛto me wɔ hɔ,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> gye sɛ Honhom Kronkron di me adanseɛ nkuro nyinaa mu ka sɛ ɛkyerɛ ne amaneɛ retwɛn me.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na memfa yei menyɛ biribi, nanso memmu me kra aboɔden memma me ho, na mede anigyeɛ mawie me nanteɛ ne ɔsom a menyaa no Awurade Yesu nkyɛn sɛ menni Nyankopɔn adom asɛmpa no ho adanseɛ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na afei, hwɛ, menim sɛ mo a menam mo mu mekaa ahennie no ho asɛm no nyinaa renhunu m’anim bio.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Enti nnɛ medi mo adanseɛ sɛ, me ho afiri mo nyinaa mogya ho;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ɛfiri sɛ mansi biribiara so, sɛ ebia merenka Nyankopɔn tiri mu agyina nyinaa menkyerɛ mo.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Enti monhwɛ mo ho ne nnwankuo nyinaa a Honhom Kronkron de mo asisi wɔn so ahwɛfoɔ, sɛ mobɛyɛne Nyankopɔn asafo a ɔde ɔno ara mogya anya wɔn no yie.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na menim sɛ, me korɔ akyiri no, mpataku bɔne bɛhyɛne mo mu a wɔrennyae nnwankuo no kwa.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Nso mo ara mo mu nnipa bɛsɔre a wɔbɛka nkontomposɛm de atwe asuafoɔ no adi wɔn akyire.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Enti monwɛn, monkae sɛ mfeɛ mmiɛnsa ni, anadwo ne awia, mennyaee mo mu biara afotuo wɔ nisuo mu da.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na afei deɛ, mede mo hyɛ Onyankopɔn nsa ne n’adom asɛm mu; ɔno na ɔbɛtumi de mo asi hɔ, na wama mo agyapadeɛ wɔn a wɔate wɔn ho nyinaa mu.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> M’ani ammere obiara dwetɛ anaa sika anaa atadeɛ.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Mo ara monim sɛ, deɛ ɛhiaa me ne wɔn a wɔka me ho no, me nsa yi ano adwuma na mede menyaeɛ.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ne nyinaa mu, mekyerɛɛ mo sɛ, ɛsɛ sɛ moyɛ adwuma saa de boa wɔn a wɔyɛ mmerɛ, na mokae Awurade Yesu nsɛm a ɔkaa sɛ: Ɔma mu wɔ nhyira sene ɔgyeɛ.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na ɔkaa saa no, ɔkotoo ne nankoroma anim ne wɔn nyinaa bɔɔ mpaeɛ.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na wɔn nyinaa suu pii, na wɔsosɔɔ Paulo kɔn fee n’ano.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Na deɛ ɛyɛɛ wɔn ya bebrebe ne asɛm a ɔkaa sɛ wɔrenhunu n’anim bio no. Na wɔkɔgyaa no kwan wɔ suhyɛn no mu."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ yɛne wɔn dii ntetemu no, yɛsii mu nam nsuo ani tee baa Ko, na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, yɛduruu Rode, na yɛfirii hɔ baa Patara.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na yɛhunuu suhyɛn bi a ɛrekɔ Foinike no, yɛkɔɔ mu, na yɛtui.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na yɛn ani tua Kipro no, yɛgya too benkum kɔɔ Siria, na yɛkɔsii fam Tiro; ɛfiri sɛ ɛhɔ na na suhyɛn no rekɔyi n’adesoa aguo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na yɛkɔhunuu asuafoɔ no no, yɛtenaa hɔ nnanson, na wɔnam Honhom no so ka kyerɛɛ Paulo sɛ ɔnnkɔ Yerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na yɛwiee nna no die no, yɛfirii hɔ tuu yɛn kwan, na wɔn nyinaa ne wɔn yerenom ne wɔn mma bɛgyaa yɛn kwan de kɔsii sɛ yɛfirii kuro no mu, na yɛkotoo mpoano hɔ bɔɔ mpaeɛ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na yɛkrakraa yɛn ho no, yɛkɔɔ suhyɛn no mu, na wɔsane kɔɔ fie.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na yɛfiri Tiro faa nsuo ani bɛduruu Ptolemai; na yɛkɔkyeaa anuanom no, yɛtenaa wɔn nkyɛn da koro.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, yɛfiri hɔ baa Kaesarea; na yɛkɔɔ Ɔsɛmpakani Filipo a ɔka baason no ho fie kɔtenaa ne nkyɛn.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔwɔ mma, mmaabunu baanan a wɔhyɛ nkɔm.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na yɛdii hɔ nna kakra no, odiyifoɔ bi a ne din de Agabo firi Yudea bae;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na ɔbaa yɛn nkyɛn no, ɔfaa Paulo abɔsoɔ de kyekyeree ne nan ne ne nsa kaa sɛ: Sɛdeɛ Honhom Kronkron seɛ ni: Ɔbarima a abɔsoɔ yi yɛ ne dea no, Yudafoɔ a wɔwɔ Yerusalem bɛkyekyere no saa ara, na wɔayi no ahyɛ amanaman nsa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na yɛtee yeinom no, yɛne wɔn a wɔwɔ hɔ no srɛɛ no sɛ ɔnnkɔ Yerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Paulo buaa sɛ: Adɛn na moresu bubu m’akoma yi? Me deɛ, masiesie me ho sɛ Awurade Yesu din nti, ɛnyɛ ɛkyerɛ nko na wɔbɛkye me, na mpo mɛwu wɔ Yerusalem hɔ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔmpene so mma yɛn no, yɛgyaee kaa sɛ: Deɛ Awurade pɛ nyɛ hɔ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na nna no akyiri no, yɛboaboaa yɛn ho kɔɔ Yerusalem.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Kaesarea asuafoɔ no mu bi nso ne yɛn kɔe, na wɔde yɛn baa Mnason, Kiproni bi a ɔyɛ osuani dada, nkyɛn sɛ yɛnkɔtena hɔ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na yɛduruu Yerusalem no, anuanom no gyee yɛn fɛ so.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, Paulo ne yɛn kɔɔ Yakobo nkyɛn, na mpanimfoɔ no nyinaa baa hɔ bi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔkyeaa wɔn no, ɔkaa deɛ Onyankopɔn nam ne som so ayɛ amanaman no mu no mmaako mmaako kyerɛɛ wɔn.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na wɔteeɛ no, wɔhyɛɛ Onyankopɔn animuonyam; na wɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ; Onua, wohunu Yudafoɔ mpempem a wɔagye adie a wɔn nyinaa bɔ mmara no ho mmɔden.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na wɔate wo ho asɛm sɛ wokyerɛkyerɛ Yudafoɔ a wɔwɔ amanaman no mu nyinaa sɛ wɔnnya Mose, na woka sɛ wɔnntwa wɔn mma twetia, na wɔnnni amanneɛ no so.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Afei yɛnyɛ no dɛn? Ɛnyɛ dɛn ara a, wɔbɛte sɛ woaba.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Enti yɛ deɛ yɛreka akyerɛ woɔ yi: Yɛwɔ mmarima baanan bi a wɔadi nseɛ.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Fa wɔn, na wo ne wɔn nkɔdwira mo ho, na tua ka ma wɔn, na wɔnyi wɔn ti; na wɔn nyinaa nhunu sɛ, wo ho nsɛm a wɔteeɛ no biara nnim, na mmom wo ara nso wonam pɛpɛɛpɛ di mmara no so.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na amanaman a wɔagye adie no ho deɛ, yɛatwerɛ, na yɛabua sɛ wɔnyi wɔn ho mfiri abosom afɔdeɛ ne mogya ne mmoa a wɔanhwie wɔn mogya na wɔwuiɛ ne adwamammɔ ho.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ɛnna Paulo faa mmarima no, na adeɛ kyeeɛ a ɔne wɔn dwiraa wɔn ho no, ɔne wɔn kɔɔ asɔrefie sɛ ɔrekɔkyerɛ ahodwira nna no wie a wɔbɛwie no, na wɔabɛbɔ afɔdeɛ ama wɔn nyinaa mmaako mmaako.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na nnanson no reyɛ aduru no, Yudafoɔ a wɔfiri Asia hunuu no asɔrefie no, wɔhwanyanee nnipa a ahyia hɔ no nyinaa maa wɔsɔɔ no mu teaa mu sɛ:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Israel mmarima, mommɛboa! Oyi ne onipa a ɔkyerɛkyerɛ nnipa nyinaa mmaa nyinaa tia ɔman ne mmara ne ɛha yi, na ɔde Helafoɔ nso aba asɔrefie, de efi abɛka kronkronbea ha yi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Nso wɔhunuu ɔne Efesoni Trofimo wɔ kuro mu hɔ kane, enti wɔdwenee sɛ gyama Paulo de no akɔ asɔrefie hɔ.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na kuro no nyinaa bɔɔ twi, na nkurɔfoɔ no de mmirika bɛboaa ano; na wɔsɔɔ Paulo mu twee no firii asɔrefie hɔ, na ntɛm ara wɔtotoo apono no mu.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na wɔrehwehwɛ aku no no, asɛm no kɔduruu asraafoɔ apem so safohene no aso mu sɛ Yerusalem nyinaa ayɛ sakasaka.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na ntɛm ara ɔfaa asraafoɔ ne ɔha so mpanimfoɔ, na ɔde mmirika kɔtoaa wɔn. Na wɔhunuu ɔsafohene ne asraafoɔ no no, wɔgyaee Paulo hweɛ.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ɛnna ɔsafohene no kɔ kɔsɔɔ ne mu, na ɔhyɛɛ sɛ wɔmfa nkɔnsɔnkɔnsɔn mmienu ngu no, na ɔbisaa onipa ko a ɔyɛ, ne deɛ wayɛ.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na nkurɔfokuo no mu binom teaa mu sɛɛ, na ebinom nso teaa mu sɛɛ. Na sakasaka no nti ɔntumi nhunu mu nokorɛ no, na ɔhyɛɛ sɛ wɔmfa no nkɔ aban mu.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na ɔduruu ntwedeɛ no soɔ no, ɛbaa sɛ nkurɔfokuo no kitikiti nti, asraafoɔ no soaa no.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na ɔman no mu nnipakuo kɛseɛ dii n’akyi teaa mu sɛ: Yi no hɔ!",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na wɔde Paulo rebɛkɔ aban no mu no, ɔbisaa ɔsafohene no sɛ: Mewɔ ho kwan sɛ meka asɛm bi mekyerɛ woɔ? Na ɔse: Wonim Hela kasa anaa?",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ɛnyɛ wone Misraimni a nnaano ɔyɛɛ sakasaka, na ɔde mmarima awudifoɔ mpemnan kɔɔ serɛ soɔ no?",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na Paulo kaa sɛ: Meyɛ Yudani a mefiri Tarso, Kilikia kuro a ɛwɔ din pa ara no mu nipa ne me. Nanso mesrɛ wo, ma me kwan na menkasa menkyerɛ ɔman no.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na ɔmaa no kwan no, Paulo gyinaa ntwedeɛ no so de ne nsa nyamm nkurɔfoɔ no; na wɔyɛɛ komm no, ɔde Hebri kasa ne wɔn kasaa sɛ:"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Anuanom ne agyanom, montie m’ano a mereyi makyerɛ mo yi!",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na wɔtee sɛ ɔrekasa Hebri kasa de kyerɛ wɔn no, wɔyɛɛ komm koraa. Na ɔse:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Meyɛ Yudani a wɔwoo me Tarso wɔ Kilikia, na wɔtetee me kuro yi mu wɔ Gamaliel nan ase, na wɔkyerɛkyerɛɛ me agyanom mmara no mu pɛ, na mebɔɔ Nyankopɔn som ho mmɔden, sɛdeɛ mo nyinaa moyɛ nnɛ yi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na metaa Ɔkwan yi de kɔɔ owuo mu. Mekyekyeree mmarima ne mmaa, na meyii wɔn maa wɔde wɔn kɔguu afiase,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> sɛdeɛ ɔsɔfo panin nso ne mpanimfoɔ nyinaa di me adanseɛ no. Wɔn nkyɛn nso na mekɔgyee nwoma sɛ mede merekɔma anuanom no, na mekɔɔ Damasko sɛ merekɔfa wɔn a wɔwɔ hɔ no nso nkyehoma mu maba Yerusalem, na wɔatwe wɔn aso.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ menam kwan so na mebɛnee Damasko no, ɛbɛyɛ awigyina no, mpofirim, hann kɛseɛ bi firi soro hyerɛn bɛtwaa me ho hyiae.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na mehwee fam, na metee nne bi a ɛsee me sɛ: Saulo, Saulo, adɛn na wotaa me?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na mebuaa sɛ: Ɛyɛ wo hwan a, Awura? Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Ɛyɛ me Yesu Nasareni a wotaa no no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na wɔn a wɔne me nam no hunuu hann no deɛ, nanso wɔante deɛ na ɔne me rekasa no nne.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na mekaa sɛ: Ɛdeɛn na menyɛ, Awurade? Na Awurade ka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Sɔre kɔ Damasko, na ɛhɔ na wɔbɛka wo adeɛ a wɔahyɛ sɛ yɛ nyinaa ho asɛm.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na hann no animuonyam amma manhunu adeɛ nti, wɔn a wɔne me nam no sosɔɔ me nsa, na wɔde me kɔɔ Damasko.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔbarima bi a wɔfrɛ no Anania a ɔyɛ nyamesuroni, sɛdeɛ mmara no teɛ, a Yudafoɔ a wɔwɔ hɔ nyinaa bɔ no din pa",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> baa me nkyɛn bɛgyinaa hɔ ka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onua Saulo, hunu adeɛ! Na ɛdɔn no ara mu no memaa m’ani soɔ mehunuu no.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔkaa sɛ: Yɛn agyanom Nyankopɔn ayi wo ato hɔ sɛ hunu ne pɛ a ɔpɛ, na hunu Ɔteneneeni no, na te nankasa ne nne.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na wobɛyɛ ne danseni, na woadi deɛ woahunu, na woateɛ ho adanseɛ akyerɛ nnipa nyinaa.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na afei, adɛn na worekyinkyim wo ho? Sɔre ma wɔmmɔ wo asu nhohoro wo bɔne, na bɔ Awurade din!",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ mesane baa Yerusalem na merebɔ mpaeɛ asɔrefie no, m’ani wiaa me maa mekɔɔ tebea foforɔ mu,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na mehunuu no, na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Ma wo ho nyɛ hare na firi Yerusalem ntɛm, ɛfiri sɛ wɔrennye w’adanseɛ a wobɛdi no me ho no.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na mekaa sɛ: Awurade, wɔn ara wɔnim sɛ wɔn a wɔgye wo die no, mede wɔn meguu afiase, na mehwee wɔn hyia adan nyinaa mu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na wɔrehwie wo danseni Stefano mogya aguo no, na me nso megyina hɔ, na mepenee so, na mehwɛɛ wɔn a wɔrekum no no ntadeɛ so.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Kɔ, na mɛsoma wo mafiri ha akɔ akyirikyiri, amanaman mu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na wɔtiee no bɛduruu asɛm yi so, na wɔmaa wɔn nne so sɛ: Yi saa onipa yi firi asase so, na ɛnsɛ sɛ ɔtena ase!",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wɔreteatea mu na wɔreto wɔn ntoma guo tu mfuturo gu ahunum no,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ɔsafohene no hyɛɛ sɛ wɔmfa no nkɔ aban mu, na ɔkaa sɛ wɔmfa mpire mmisa no, na ɔnhunu adekodeɛ a enti wɔbom gu ne soɔ yi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na wɔde nhoma kyekyeree no no, Paulo bisaa ɔha so panin a ɔgyina hɔ no sɛ: Mowɔ ho kwan sɛ moka onipa a ɔyɛ Romani na wɔmmuu no fɔ mpire anaa?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na ɔha so panin no tee saa no, ɔkɔka kyerɛɛ ɔsafohene no sɛ: Ɛdeɛn na worebɛyɛ yi? Hwɛ, onipa yi yɛ Romani.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ɔsafohene no ba bɛbisaa no sɛ: Woyɛ Romani a, ka kyerɛ me! Na Paulo se: Aane.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na ɔsafohene no buaa sɛ: Me deɛ, ɔmanbayɛ yi, mede sika pii na ɛtɔeɛ. Na Paulo se: Me deɛ, wɔde woo me.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ɛnna ntɛm ara wɔn a wɔrebɛbisa no no firii ne nkyɛn. Na ɔsafohene no tee sɛ ɔyɛ Romani no, ɔsuroo sɛ wakyekyere no.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, na ɔpɛɛ sɛ ɔhunu adekodeɛ a enti Yudafoɔ totoo n’ano no mu nokorɛ nti, ɔsanee no firii ne nkyehoma mu, na ɔhyɛɛ sɛ asɔfoɔ mpanimfoɔ ne wɔn badwafoɔ nyinaa mmra, na ɔmaa wɔde Paulo ba bɛgyinaa wɔn anim."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Paulo gyenee n’ani hwɛɛ abadwafoɔ no kaa sɛ: Anuanom, me deɛ, ahonim pa nyinaa na mede mabɔ me bra mama Onyankopɔn de abɛsi ɛnnɛ da yi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na Ɔsɔfopanin Anania hyɛɛ wɔn a wɔgyina ne ho sɛ wɔmmɔ n’ano so.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ɛnna Paulo ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Bɔ na Onyankopɔn bɛbɔ woɔ, wo ɔfasuo a wɔahoa ho; na wote hɔ rebu me atɛn sɛdeɛ mmara no teɛ, nanso wobu mmara no so hyɛ sɛ wɔmmɔ me?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na wɔn a wɔgyina hɔ no kaa sɛ: Nyankopɔn sɔfo panin na woya no yi?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɛnna Paulo kaa sɛ: Anuanom, mennim sɛ ɔyɛ ɔsɔfo panin; ɛfiri sɛ wɔatwerɛ sɛ: Nka wo man panin ho asɛm bɔne!",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Paulo hunuu sɛ nnipa no fa yɛ Sadukifoɔ, na ɔfa nso yɛ Farisifoɔ no, ɔteaa mu badwa mu hɔ sɛ: Anuanom, meyɛ Farisini ne Farisifoɔ ba; awufoɔ sɔreɛ ne ɛho anidasoɔ nti na wɔrebu me atɛn yi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔkaa saa no, akasakasa baa Farisifoɔ ne Sadukifoɔ no ntam, na nnipakuo no mu paee.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ Sadukifoɔ ka sɛ awufoɔ sɔreɛ, anaa ɔbɔfoɔ, anaa honhom nni hɔ, na Farisifoɔ deɛ, wɔgye ne nyinaa di.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na wɔteateaa mu kɛseɛ, na Atwerɛfoɔ a wɔwɔ Farisifoɔ afa no sɔre kasakasaa sɛ: Yɛnhunu bɔne biara wɔ onipa yi mu; na sɛ honhom anaa ɔbɔfoɔ akasa akyerɛ no ɛ?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na akasakasa no mu yɛɛ den no, ɔsafohene no suroo sɛ ebia wɔbɛtete Paulo mu nti, ɔhyɛɛ asraafoɔ no sɛ wɔnsiane mmɛhwim no mfiri wɔn nsam, na wɔmfa no nkɔ aban mu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na anadwo no, Awurade bɛgyinaa ne nkyɛn kaa sɛ: Ma wo bo nyɛ duru; na sɛdeɛ woadi me ho adanseɛ Yerusalem ha yi no, saa ara nso na ɛsɛ sɛ wokɔdi adanseɛ wɔ Roma.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, Yudafoɔ no mu binom pam kekaa wɔn ho ntam sɛ wɔrennidi, nanso wɔrennom, gye sɛ wɔakum Paulo ansa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na wɔn a wɔbɔɔ mu pamm ne tiri soɔ yi bɛboro aduanan.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔbaa asɔfoɔ mpanimfoɔ ne mpanimfoɔ no nkyɛn bɛkaa sɛ: Yɛakeka yɛn ho ntam sɛ hwee renka yɛn ano, gye sɛ yɛakum Paulo ansa.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Enti afei mo ne badwafoɔ nkɔbɔ din nkyerɛ ɔsafohene no, na ɔmfa no mmrɛ mo, sɛdeɛ morebɛbisa ne ho asɛm no mu yie; na yɛn deɛ, ansa na ɔbɛduru ha no, yɛbɛku no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Paulo wɔfase tee wɔn tɛ no, ɔkɔ kɔhyɛnee aban no mu kɔyii Paulo asotire.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Paulo frɛɛ ɔha so mpanimfoɔ no mu baako kaa sɛ: Fa aberanteɛ yi kɔ ɔsafohene nkyɛn; na ɔwɔ asɛm bi ka kyerɛ no.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ɛnna ɔfaa no de no kɔɔ ɔsafohene no nkyɛn kaa sɛ: Ɔdeduani Paulo frɛɛ me srɛɛ me sɛ memfa aberanteɛ yi mmra wo nkyɛn, na ɔwɔ asɛm bi ka kyerɛ wo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔsafohene no sɔɔ ne nsa, na ɔne no kɔɔ fa baabi, na ɔbisaa sɛ: Ɛdeɛn na wowɔ ka kyerɛ me?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na ɔse: Yudafoɔ apam sɛ wɔbɛsrɛ wo, na ɔkyena wode Paulo asiane aba edwam sɛdeɛ wɔrebɛbisa ne ho asɛm mu yie.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Nanso ntie wɔn! Na wɔn mu mmarima bɛboro aduanan retɛ no; na wɔakeka wɔn ho ntam sɛ wɔrennidi, na wɔrennom, gye sɛ wɔakum no ansa; na afei wɔasiesie wɔn ho, na wɔretwɛn sɛ wobɛma ho kwan.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ɛnna ɔsafohene no gyaa aberanteɛ no kwan, na ɔhyɛɛ no sɛ: Nka nkyerɛ obiara sɛ woayi me asotire!",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ɔfrɛɛ asraafoɔ ɔha so mpanimfoɔ no mu baanu bi kaa sɛ: Monsiesie asraafoɔ ahanu na wɔnkɔ Kaesarea, ne apɔnkɔfoɔ aduɔson, ne mpɛmɛtofoɔ ahanu, anadwo bɛyɛ nnɔnkron berɛ mu.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na wɔnsiesie mmoa nso, na wɔmfa Paulo ntena so, mfa no dwoodwoo nkɔma Amrado Felike.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɔtwerɛɛ nwoma a emu asɛm se:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Klaudio Lisia de yei kyea amrado pa Felike.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ɔbarima yi a Yudafoɔ kɔfaa no sɛ anka wɔbɛkum no na me ne dɔm kɔ kɔhwimm no no, mate sɛ ɔyɛ Romani.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na mepɛɛ sɛ anka mehunu adekodeɛ a wɔde reto ne soɔ no, mede no mekɔɔ wɔn dwa mu;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> na mehunuu sɛ wɔn mmara ho asɛmmisa nti na wɔne no wɔ nkuro, na wɔamfa biribi a ɛsɛ owuo anaa ɔkyerɛ anto no so.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Nanso wɔayi me asotire sɛ, nnipa bi retɛ ɔbarima no nti, merema wɔde no abrɛ wo, na mahyɛ ne nkurobɔfoɔ no nso sɛ wɔmmɛka deɛ wɔwɔ wɔ ne ho no wɔ w’anim.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ɛnna asraafoɔ no faa Paulo, sɛdeɛ wɔhyɛɛ wɔn no, na wɔde no kɔɔ Antipatri anadwo no.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, wɔmaa apɔnkɔfoɔ no ne no kɔe, na wɔsane baa aban no mu bio.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na wɔn deɛ, wɔduruu Kaesarea na wɔyii nwoma no maa amrado no, wɔde Paulo nso kɔgyinaa n’anim.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na amrado no kenkan nwoma no wieeɛ, na ɔbisaa ɔman ko a ɔfiri mu, na ɔtee sɛ ɔfiri Kilikia no,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> ɔkaa sɛ: Wo nkurobɔfoɔ no ba a, na mɛtie woɔ. Na ɔhyɛɛ sɛ wɔmfa no nsie Herode aban mu."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ne nnannum soɔ no, Ɔsɔfopanin Anania ne mpanimfoɔ bi ne mmaranimfoɔ bi a ɔde Tertulo bae, na wɔbɛbɔɔ Paulo kwaadu kyerɛɛ amrado no.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na wɔfrɛɛ no no, Tertulo firii aseɛ bɔɔ nkuro sɛ: Ɛsiane sɛ wo nti yɛanya asomdwoeɛ bebree ne ntotoeɛ a ɛnam wo nimdeɛ so aba ɔman yi mu nti,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Felike, onimuonyamfoɔ, yɛde aseda gye daa wɔ mmaa nyinaa.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na mempɛ sɛ yɛsɛe wo berɛ pii nti, mesrɛ wo, fa wo ara w’ayamyie no tie yɛn kakraa bi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Yɛahunu ɔbarima yi sɛ ɔyɛ obusufoɔ a ɔde mansotwe ba Yudafoɔ a wɔwɔ wiase nyinaa mu, na ɔyɛ Nasarefoɔ fekuo no mu panin.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔsɔ hwɛɛ sɛ ɔde efi bɛka asɔrefie nso na yɛkɔkyeree no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> [Na anka yɛpɛɛ sɛ yɛfa yɛn mmara so bu no atɛn; na Ɔsafohene Lisia bae de aniɛden bɛgyee no yɛn nsam de no kɔe, na ɔhyɛɛ wɔn a wɔne no wɔ nkuro no sɛ wɔmmra wo nkyɛn;]",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> enti wo ara wobisa no a, wobɛhunu deɛ enti a yɛne no rebɔ nkuro yi nyinaa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Yudafoɔ no nso foaa no so sɛ nsɛm yi te saa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na amrado no nyamm Paulo sɛ ɔnkasa no, ɔbuaa sɛ: Ɛsiane sɛ menim sɛ wofiri yɛɛ ɔman yi temmufoɔ adi mfirinhyia pii nti, mede akoma pa mereyi m’ano.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Wobɛtumi ahunu sɛ ɛmmoroo dadu nnammienu na mekɔɔ Yerusalem sɛ merekɔsɔre.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wɔanhu me asɔrefie anaa hyia adan mu anaa kuro mu hɔ sɛ me ne obi rekasa, anaasɛ merehwanyan nkurɔfoɔ no mu,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> nanso wɔrentumi nkyerɛ me nnoɔma a enti wɔretoto m’ano yi ase.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na yei deɛ, mepae mu meka mekyerɛ wo sɛ Ɔkwan a wɔfrɛ no sɛ Fekuo no mu na mesɔre m’agyanom Nyankopɔn, na megye nnoɔma a wɔatwerɛ no mmara ne adiyifoɔ mu nyinaa medi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na mewɔ Nyankopɔn ho anidasoɔ a wɔn ara nso wɔhwɛ no kwan, sɛ owusɔreɛ a wɔn a wɔtene ne wɔn a wɔntene bɛsɔre no bɛba.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na yei mu na mesɔ me ho mehwɛ, sɛ mɛnya ahonim a ɛnni fɔ Nyankopɔn ne nnipa fam daa.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na mfirinhyia bebree akyiri no, mebaa sɛ mede ayɛyɛdeɛ merebrɛ me man na mabɛbɔ afɔdeɛ;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ɛno mu na wɔhunuu me sɛ meredwira me ho asɔrefie hɔ, nso ɛnyɛ me ne nkurɔfokuo, anaasɛ meyɛɛ gyegyeegye biara.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɛyɛ Yudafoɔ bi a wɔfiri Asia, wɔn na anka ɛsɛ sɛ wɔba w’anim ha, na sɛ wɔwɔ me ho asɛm bi a, wɔne me abɛbɔ nkuro.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Anaasɛ ma wɔnka sɛ megyina badwafoɔ no anim no, wɔhunuu me ho adeɛ a ɛntene bi anaa,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> gye asɛm baako yi a megyina wɔn mu no, meteaa mu mekaa sɛ: Awufoɔ sɔreɛ ho na morebu me atɛn nnɛ yi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Felike nim Ɔkwan no ho asɛm no mu yie nti, ɔkaa sɛ montwentwɛn so kakra na sɛ: Ɔsafohene Lisia ba a, na mɛtie asɛm no mu yie.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ɔhyɛɛ asraafoɔ ɔha so panin no sɛ ɔmfa no nsie, na wɔnnyɛ no biribiara, na ne ho nnipa bi bɛsom no anaasɛ ɔba ne nkyɛn a, ɔnnkame no.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na nna bi akyiri no, Felike ne ne yere Drusila a ɔyɛ Yudani bae, na ɔsoma maa wɔkɔfrɛɛ Paulo baeɛ, na wɔtiee Kristo Yesu mu gyidie no ho asɛm.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɔreka tenenee ne anidahɔ ne atemmuo a ɛreba no ho asɛm no, Felike suroe, na ɔkaa sɛ: Seesei deɛ, kɔ, na menya adagyeɛ a, mɛma wɔabɛfrɛ wo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na n’ani da so nso sɛ Paulo bɛma no sika na wagyaa no; enti na daa ɔma wɔkɔfrɛ no, na ɔne no bɔ nkɔmmɔ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na mfirinhyia mmienu duruiɛ no, Porkio Festo bɛsii Felike ananmu; na Felike pɛɛ sɛ ɔsɔ Yudafoɔ ani nti, ɔgyaa Paulo wɔ afiase hɔ."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na afei Festo baa ne man a ɔdi so amrado no mu, na nnansa akyiri no, ɔfiri Kaesarea kɔɔ Yerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na asɔfoɔ mpanimfoɔ ne Yudafoɔ no bɛbɔɔ Paulo ho kwaadu kyerɛɛ no,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na wɔsrɛɛ no sɛ ɔnnom wɔn, na ɔnsoma nkɔfa no mmra Yerusalem; na anka wɔatɛ no kwan so akum no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na Festo buaa sɛ Paulo ntena Kaesarea, na ɛrenkyɛ na ɔno ara akɔ hɔ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔkaa sɛ: Enti momma mo mu atitire ne me nkɔ, na sɛ ɔbarima yi ho wɔ asɛm bi a, wɔne no nkɔbɔ nkuro.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔdii wɔn nkyɛn bɛyɛ nnawɔtwe anaa dadu no, ɔsiane kɔɔ Kaesarea. Na adeɛ kyeeɛ a ɔkɔtenaa asɛnnie adwa soɔ no, ɔhyɛɛ sɛ wɔmfa Paulo mmra.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔbaeɛ no, Yudafoɔ a wɔfiri Yerusalem baeɛ no bɛtwaa ne ho kanko, na wɔkaa ne ho nsɛmmɔne pii a emu yɛ duru a wɔantumi ankyerɛ aseɛ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Paulo yii ano sɛ: Menyɛɛ Yudafoɔ mmara anaa asɔrefie anaa Kaesare ho bɔne biara.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na Festo pɛ sɛ ɔsɔ Yudafoɔ ani nti, ɔbisaa Paulo sɛ: Wopɛ sɛ wokɔ Yerusalem, na wɔabu wo nnoɔma yi ho atɛn m’anim wɔ hɔ?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na Paulo kaa sɛ: Kaesare asɛnnie adwa anim na megyina, na ɛha na ɛsɛ sɛ wɔbu me atɛn, na Yudafoɔ deɛ, menyɛɛ wɔn bɔne biara, sɛdeɛ wo nso wonim yie.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na sɛ medi fɔ anaasɛ mayɛ biribi a ɛsɛ owuo a, menhwehwɛ sɛ owuo no bɛpare me; na sɛ nnoɔma a wɔde rebɔ me kwaadu yi mu biara nyɛ nokorɛ a, obiara ntumi mfa me nhyɛ wɔn nsa. Ɛnneɛ mede asɛm no medane Kaesare.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛnna Festo ne abadwafoɔ no kasaeɛ no, ɔbuaa sɛ: Sɛ wode akɔdane Kaesare a, ɛnneɛ Kaesare anim na wobɛkorɔ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na nna bi twaa mu no, Ɔhene Agripa ne Berenike baa Kaesarea bɛkyeaa Festo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔkyɛree hɔ nti, Festo kaa Paulo ho asɛm no kyerɛɛ ɔhene no sɛ: Ɔbarima bi wɔ hɔ a Felike agya no mpokyerɛ mu;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na mekɔɔ Yerusalem no, asɔfoɔ mpanimfoɔ ne Yudafoɔ mpanimfoɔ bɛbɔɔ no kwaadu kyerɛɛ me, srɛɛ me sɛ memmu no atɛn.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na mebuaa wɔn sɛ ɛnyɛ Romafoɔ amanneɛ sɛ wɔbɛyi onipa bi ama, gye sɛ nkurobɔfoɔ no ne deɛ wɔne no wɔ nkuro no hyia, na ɔnya kwan yi deɛ wɔde ato no soɔ no ano ansa.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Enti wɔbɛhyiaa ha no, mantwe asɛm no anto hɔ, na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, mekɔtenaa asɛnnie adwa so, na mehyɛɛ sɛ wɔmfa onipa no mmra.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ne nkurobɔfoɔ no bɛgyinaa ne ho no, wɔanka nsɛm a mesusuiɛ no mu biara anto ne so,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na mmom wɔn ara nyamesom ho akyinnyeɛ bi na wɔne no gyeeɛ, ɛne Yesu bi a wawu a Paulo ka sɛ, ɔte aseɛ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na ɛnam sɛ menhunu sɛdeɛ mɛhwehwɛ saa akyinnyegyeɛ yi mu nti, mebisaa no sɛ ɔbɛkɔ Yerusalem na wɔakɔbu no nsɛm yi ho atɛn anaa?",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Paulo srɛɛ sɛ wɔmfa no nhyɛ afiase ntwɛn Ɔhempɔn no ano asɛm. Yei nti mehyɛɛ sɛ wɔmfa no nsie kɔsi sɛ mede no bɛkɔ Kaesare anim.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na Agripa ka kyerɛɛ Festo sɛ: Anka me nso mepɛ sɛ metie onipa no. Na ɔse: Ɔkyena wobɛtie no.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Enti adeɛ kyeeɛ no, Agripa ne Berenike de ahokeka a ɛte apɔ bae, na wɔne asafohene ne kuro mu hɔ nnipa a wɔwɔ din kɔɔ faako a wɔtie asɛm no, na Festo hyɛeɛ no, wɔde Paulo bae.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na Festo kaa sɛ: Ɔhene Agripa ne mmarima a mo ne yɛn wɔ ha yi nyinaa, moahunu deɛ Yudafoɔ nyinaa de n’asɛm aba m’anim Yerusalem ne ɛha yi, na wɔka sɛ ɛnsɛ no sɛ ɔtena ase bio no.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Mahunu sɛ ɔnyɛɛ biribiara a ɛsɛ wuo, nanso ɔno ara de asɛm no akɔdane Ɔhempɔn nti, mahyɛ sɛ mɛma wɔde no akɔ hɔ.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Nanso menni ne ho asɛm titire bi a mɛtwerɛ makɔma me wura; enti na mede no maba mo anim, ne titire no, Ɔhene Agripa anim, na sɛ wɔnya hunu asɛm no mu a, manya biribi matwerɛ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ɛyɛ me sɛ nyansa biara nnim sɛ mema wɔde ɔdeduani bɛkorɔ, na menkyerɛ asɛm ko a wɔde ato ne soɔ."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Agripa ka kyerɛɛ Paulo sɛ: Wɔama wo kwan sɛ ka w’asɛm. Ɛnna Paulo tenee ne nsa yii ano sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Mebu no sɛ ɛyɛ akwannya ma me sɛ merebɛyi m’ano nnɛ wɔ wo Ɔhene Agripa anim, wɔ nnoɔma a Yudafoɔ de toto m’ano nyinaa ho,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ne titire no, wonim amanneɛ nyinaa ne akyinnyesɛm a ɛwɔ Yudafoɔ mu; enti mesrɛ wo sɛ tɔ wo bo ase tie me.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> M’asetena a ɛfiri me mmɔfraase no deɛ, sɛdeɛ ɛfirii aseɛ na ɛteɛ me manfoɔ mu wɔ Yerusalem no, Yudafoɔ nyinaa nim.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na wɔnim me firi mfitiaseɛ dada, nso sɛ wɔpɛ sɛ wɔdi ɛho adanseɛ a, wɔnim me sɛ mefraa fekuo a wɔdi yɛn som so pɛpɛɛpɛ no mu, mebɔɔ me bra sɛ Farisini.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na afei megyina ha, na wɔrebu me atɛn Nyankopɔn bɔ a ɔhyɛɛ yɛn agyanom no ho anidasoɔ nti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ɛno ara na yɛn mmusuakuo dummienu no de awia ne anadwo som, a emu yɛ den, ma wɔn ani da so sɛ wɔbɛnya. Ɔhene, saa anidasoɔ yi nti na Yudafoɔ toto m’ano yi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Adɛn nti na mobu yei asɛm a wɔnnye nnie sɛ Onyankopɔn nyane awufoɔ?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ɛwɔ mu sɛ ɛyɛɛ me ara nso sɛ, ɛsɛ me sɛ meyɛ nnoɔma pii metia Yesu Nasareni no din;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ɛno nso na meyɛɛ no Yerusalem, na menyaa asɔfoɔ mpanimfoɔ nkyɛn tumi no, mede ahotefoɔ bebree meguu afiase. Na wɔrekum wɔn a, mede m’ano meto mu bi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na metaa metwee wɔn aso hyia adan nyinaa mu, na mehyɛɛ wɔn maa wɔkaa abususɛm, na m’ani beree wɔn so papaapa nti, metaa wɔn kɔduruu ananafoɔ nkuro so.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛno mu na menam sɛ merekɔ Damasko, na asɔfoɔ mpanimfoɔ ama me tumi ne ɛho kwan.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na awigyina, ɔhene, ɛkwan so no, mehunuu hann bi a ɛkyɛne owia hran sɛ ɛfiri soro abɛtwa me ne wɔn a wɔne me nam no ho ahyia.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na yɛn nyinaa hwehwee aseɛ no, metee nne bi a ɛkasa kyerɛɛ me Hebri kasa mu sɛ: Saulo, Saulo, adɛn nti na wotaa me? Ɛyɛ den ma wo sɛ wobɛto ɔkafoɔ poma ano dadeɛ kotie.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na mese: Ɛyɛ wo hwan a, Awura? Na Awurade kaa sɛ: Ɛyɛ me Yesu a wotaa no no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na sɔre gyina wo nan so; na yei nti na meyii me ho mekyerɛɛ woɔ, sɛ mɛyi wo mayɛ wo nnoɔma a woahu me wɔ mu ne deɛ merebɛyi me ho makyerɛ wo wɔ mu no ho somfoɔ ne danseni.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na mɛgye wo mafiri ɔman no ne amanaman a meresoma wo wɔn nkyɛn no nsam.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na woabue wɔn ani, na wɔadane afiri sum mu aba hann mu, na wɔafiri Satan tumi ase aba Nyankopɔn nkyɛn, na wɔanya bɔne fakyɛ ne agyapadeɛ, wɔn a wɔde gyeɛ a wɔgye me die no ate wɔn ho no mu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Enti, Ɔhene Agripa, manyɛ ɔsoro adeɛ a wɔyi kyerɛɛ me no ho asoɔden,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na meka mekyerɛɛ wɔn a wɔwɔ Damasko kane, ne wɔn a wɔwɔ Yerusalem ne Yudea asase nyinaa so, ne amanaman no, sɛ wɔnsakyera wɔn adwene, na wɔnnane mmra Nyankopɔn nkyɛn, na wɔnyɛ nnwuma a ɛsɛ adwensakyera.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Yei nti na Yudafoɔ bɛkyeree me asɔrefie hwehwɛɛ sɛ wɔku me.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ɛnam sɛ Onyankopɔn di m’akyire nti, na megyina hɔ de abɛduru nnɛ yi, na medi nnipa nketewa ne akɛseɛ adanseɛ, na menka biribiara sɛ deɛ adiyifoɔ ne Mose kaa sɛ ɛbɛba no:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Sɛ Kristo no bɛhunu amane, na wadi awufoɔ sɔreɛ mu kan ama wɔaka hann ho asɛm akyerɛ ɔman no ne amanaman mufoɔ no.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ɔyii n’ano saa no, Festo de nne kɛseɛ kaa sɛ: Paulo, woabɔ dam, nwomanim bebrebe abɔ wo dam.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɔse: Memmɔɔ dam, Onimuonyamfoɔ Festo, na meka nokorɛ ne anidahɔ nsɛm.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na ɔhene a mede nnam meka mekyerɛ no yi nim nsɛm yi mu; na megye medi sɛ yeinom biara nhuntaa no, ɛfiri sɛ wɔanyɛ yei kokoa mu.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ɔhene Agripa, wogye adiyifoɔ di anaa? Menim sɛ wogye di.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na Agripa ka kyerɛɛ Paulo sɛ: Wopɛ sɛ wode ɛberɛ kakraa bi ma me dane bɛyɛ Okristoni anaa?",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na Paulo se: Anka mepɛ Nyankopɔn fam sɛ, kakraa bi oo, bebree oo, ɛnyɛ wo nko, na mmom wɔn a wɔretie me nnɛ yi nyinaa nso nyɛ sɛ me ara, gye mpokyerɛ yi nko mu.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na ɔhene ne amrado ne Berenike ne wɔn a wɔne wɔn te hɔ no sɔreeɛ,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> na wɔkɔɔ nkyɛn baabi no, wɔsesee wɔn ho sɛ: Onipa yi nyɛɛ biribi a ɛsɛ wuo anaa ɛkyerɛ.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na Agripa ka kyerɛɛ Festo sɛ: Sɛ onipa yi amfa n’asɛm ankɔdane Kaesare a, anka wɔbɛtumi agyaa no."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na wɔsii agyinaeɛ sɛ yɛnkɔ Italia no, wɔyii Paulo ne apokyerɛfoɔ bi maa asraafoɔ ha so panin bi a ne din de Yulio, a ɔfiri Augustan asraafoɔ kuo mu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na yɛkɔɔ Adramitio suhyɛn bi a ɛrebɛkɔ Asia fam mu no, yɛtui, na Makedoniani Aristarko a ɔfiri Tesalonika ka yɛn ho.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, yɛkɔgyinaa Sidon. Na Yulio yɛɛ Paulo adɔeɛ maa no kwan sɛ ɔnkɔ ne nnamfonom nkyɛn mma wɔnhwɛ no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na yɛtu firii hɔnom no, yɛfaa Kipro aseɛ aseɛ, ɛfiri sɛ mframa hyiaa yɛn.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na yɛfaa Kilikia ne Pamfilia po soɔ no, yɛkɔgyinaa Likia kuro Mira ho.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɛhɔ na asraafoɔ ɔha so panin no hunuu Aleksandria suhyɛn bi a ɛrekɔ Italia no, ɔde yɛn kɔguu mu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na nnafua bebree na yɛnam brɛɛ, na yɛbrɛe ansa na yɛrebɛn Knido, na mframa amma yɛn ho kwan nti, yɛfaa Kreta aseɛ aseɛ sianee Salmone ho.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na yɛnam ano ano resiane ho no, yɛbrɛɛ mu ansa na yɛreduru baabi a wɔfrɛ hɔ Hyɛn-Agyinayie a Lasea kuro bɛn ho.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɛsiane sɛ na berɛ kɔ pii, na Abuadadie atwa mu dada ma akwantuo no ayɛ hu nti, Paulo tuu wɔn fo",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> see wɔn sɛ: Mmarima, mehunu sɛ akwantuo yi rekɔyɛ sɛ deɛ amaneɛ ne adesɛeɛ bebree bɛba mu, ɛnyɛ adwadeɛ ne suhyɛn yi fam nko ara, na yɛn nkwa nso ka ho bi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nanso asraafoɔ ɔha so panin no gyee suhyɛn kwankyerɛfoɔ ne suhyɛn wura no diiɛ kyɛnee deɛ Paulo kaeɛ no.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɛsiane sɛ suhyɛn gyinaberɛ hɔ nna hɔ yie, sɛ wɔbɛdi awɔ berɛ wɔ hɔ nti, wɔn mu bebree kaa sɛ wɔbɛtu afiri hɔ nso akɔhwɛ sɛ wɔbɛtumi akɔduru Foinike a ɛyɛ Kreta suhyɛn gyinaberɛ a ɛda kɔ atifi ne atɔeɛ ntam, ɛne anafoɔ ne atɔeɛ ntam, na wɔakɔdi awɔ berɛ no wɔ hɔ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na anafoɔ mframa firii aseɛ bɔeɛ no, ɛyɛɛ wɔn sɛ wɔn nsa aka deɛ wɔde sii wɔn anim no, na wɔtuu sɛkyɛ no nam ano ano a wɔbɛnee Kreta.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ankyɛ, na mframa kɛseɛ bi a wɔfrɛ no Atifi-Apueeɛ-Mframa faa Kreta so bɛbɔeɛ;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na ɛkyeree hyɛn no, na ɛntumi nhyia mframa no, yɛmaa no twee yɛn.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na yɛde mmirika kɔfaa supɔ ketewa bi a wɔfrɛ no Klauda aseɛ no, yɛbɔɔ mmɔden ansa na yɛresosɔ kodoɔ no mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na wɔmaa soɔ no, wɔboa maa wɔkyekyeree hyɛn no; na wɔsuro sɛ ebia wɔbɛkɔ akɔhwe Anweatam no so nti, wɔhwann hyɛndua no, na ɛtwee wɔn saa.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na mframa no bɔɔ dendeenden de yɛn kyinkyiniiɛ, na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, wɔtotoo hyɛn no mu nnoɔma bi gui.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ne nnansa soɔ no, wɔde wɔn ara nsa totoo hyɛn no ho nnoɔma no twenee.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na nnafua bebree na owia anaa nsoromma mpueeɛ, nso na mframa a ɛrebɔ yɛn nyɛ adewa, enti yɛn nkwagyeɛ ho anidasoɔ nyinaa yerae.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na nna bebree twaa mu a wɔnnidie no, Paulo sɔre gyinaa wɔn mfimfini kaa sɛ: Mmarima, ɛsɛ sɛ anka motie me, na yɛamfiri Kreta ammɛhunu amane ne adesɛeɛ yi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na afei metu mo fo sɛ momma mo bo ntɔ mo yam, na mo mu biara renhwere ne nkwa, gye suhyɛn yi nko na ɛbɛsɛe.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na anadwo yi, Onyankopɔn a meyɛ ne dea na mesom no no bɔfoɔ bɛgyinaa me nkyɛn",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> kaa sɛ: Paulo, nsuro! Ɛtwa sɛ wokɔgyina Kaesare anim; na hwɛ, Onyankopɔn de wɔn a wɔne wo nam no nyinaa akyɛ wo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Enti, mmarima, momma mo bo ntɔ mo yam, na megye Onyankopɔn medi sɛ ɛbɛyɛ hɔ sɛdeɛ wɔaka akyerɛ me no;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> nanso ɛtwa sɛ yɛkɔgu supɔ bi soɔ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na dadu nnanan duruiɛ na yɛredi akɔneaba Adria po soɔ no, ɛbɛyɛ dasuo mu na suhyɛn no mu adwumayɛfoɔ no hunuu sɛ wɔrebɛn asase bi.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na wɔtoo susuhoma, na wɔhunuu sɛ ɛsi abasam aduonu; na wɔkɔɔ wɔn anim kakra no, wɔtoo bio, na wɔhunuu no abasam dunum.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na wɔsuroo sɛ ebia yɛbɛkɔ akɔhwe abotan bi so nti, wɔtoo asɛkyɛ nnan firii hyɛn no to twɛnee adekyeeɛ.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na ɛsiane sɛ na suhyɛn mu adwumayɛfoɔ no rehwehwɛ adwane afiri suhyɛn no mu nti, wɔgyaa kodoɔ no mu too po mu, yɛɛ sɛdeɛ wɔrekɔto sɛkyɛ afiri hyɛn no tiri nso no,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Paulo ka kyerɛɛ asraafoɔ ɔha so panin ne asraafoɔ no sɛ: Sɛ yeinom antena hyɛn yi mu deɛ a, morennya nkwa.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ɛnna asraafoɔ no twaa kodoɔ no ntampehoma no, na wɔmaa no kɔeɛ.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na adeɛ rebɛkye no, Paulo srɛɛ wɔn nyinaa sɛ wɔnnidi, na ɔkaa sɛ: Dadu nnanan ni a moatena hɔ adi mmuada a momfaa biribi nkaa mo ano.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Enti mesrɛ mo sɛ monnidi, na ɛno nso bɛgye mo nkwa bi. Na mo mu biara nwi baako mpo rentu mfiri ne tiri so ntɔ.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na ɔkaa saa na ɔfaa paanoo no, ɔdaa Onyankopɔn ase wɔn nyinaa anim, na ɔbubu firii aseɛ diiɛ.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na wɔn nyinaa bo tɔɔ wɔn yam, na wɔn nso faa bi diiɛ.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> (Na yɛn a yɛwɔ suhyɛn no mu nyinaa yɛ nnipa ahanu aduɔson nsia.)",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Na wɔdidi meeɛ no, wɔtoo aduane no guu po mu maa suhyɛn no mu yɛɛ hare.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, na wɔnnim asase no. Na wɔhunuu dɔnnɔn bi a ne mpoano da fam; ɛno mu na wɔsusuu sɛ wɔbɛtumi a, wɔbɛtwe suhyɛn no akorɔ.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na wɔtwaa asɛkyɛ no ahoma mu gyaa mu guu po mu, na wɔsanee akyerɛkyerɛkwan no ahoma, na wɔsii hyɛn no anim abrannaa maa mframa a ɛbɔeɛ no pia kɔɔ mpoano.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Na wɔkɔpemm nsuo mu anweatam bi no, wɔde suhyɛn no kɔtaee, na etire kɔtimii, na ɛkaa hɔ pintinn, na ɛtoɔ deɛ, asorɔkyeɛ a na ɛrebɔ denden no bubui.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na asraafoɔ no tuu agyina sɛ wɔbɛkum nneduafoɔ no, na obi annware annwane.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Nanso asraafoɔ ɔha so panin no pɛ sɛ ɔgye Paulo nti, wamma wɔanyɛ deɛ wɔsusuiɛ no, na ɔhyɛɛ sɛ wɔn a wɔbɛtumi adwareɛ mfa wɔn ho ngu po mu kane nsi fam.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Na wɔn a aka no deɛ, ebinom butubutuu ntaaboɔ so, na ebinom nso butubutuu suhyɛn nnua asinasini no bi so. Na sɛdeɛ ɛyɛeɛ na yɛn nyinaa nyaa nkwa sii fam ne no."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na yɛfirii mu firiiɛ no, ɛno na yɛtee sɛ wɔfrɛ supɔ no Malta.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na nnipa a wɔwɔ hɔ no yɛɛ yɛn adɔeɛ kɛseɛ; na osuo a ɛretɔ ne awɔ no nti, wɔsɔɔ ogya maa yɛn gyee yɛn nyinaa fɛ so.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Paulo boaboaa mmabowa ano de guu ogya no soɔ no, ɔhyeɛ no nti, ahuritia bi firii mu bɛbankyeree ne nsa ho.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na nnipa a wɔwɔ hɔ no hunuu aboa no sɛ ɔsɛne ne nsa ho no, wɔsesee wɔn ho wɔn ho sɛ: Ampa ara, onipa yi yɛ owudini a wanya nkwa afiri ɛpo mu deɛ, nanso aweretɔ nti, ɛremma no nnya nkwa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔpetee aboa no too ogya mu, nso hwee anyɛ no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na wɔn deɛ, na wɔn ani da so sɛ Paulo rebɛhonhono anaasɛ ɔrebɛhwe ase awu mpofirim; nanso wɔhwɛe hwɛeɛ na wɔhunuu sɛ biribiara anyɛ no no, wɔsesaa wɔn adwene kaa sɛ gyama ɔyɛ onyame bi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nso ɛhɔnom ara na supɔ no so otitire a ne din de Publio no asase wɔ; na ɔgyee yɛn, yɛɛ yɛn hɔhoɔ nnansa, hwɛɛ yɛn yie.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ na Publio n’agya da hɔ yare huraeɛ ne konkurowa; enti Paulo kɔɔ ne nkyɛn, na ɔbɔɔ mpaeɛ, de ne nsa guu ne so saa no yadeɛ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Yei akyiri no, wɔn a aka nso a wɔyare supɔ no soɔ no bae, maa ɔsaa wɔn yadeɛ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Wɔdii yɛn ni pii, na yɛfiri hɔ rekorɔ no, wɔde nnoɔma a ɛhia yɛn no brɛɛ yɛn.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na abosome mmiɛnsa akyiri no, yɛfaa Aleksandria suhyɛn bi a ɛbɛdii awɔ berɛ supɔ no so a ne nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ ne Ata-ne-Ata no mu kɔe.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na yɛkɔgyinaa Sirakuse no, yɛdii hɔ nnansa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ɛhɔ na yɛfiri konton kɔduruu Regio, na dafua akyiri no, anafoɔ mframa bɔe, na adeɛ kyeeɛ no, yɛkɔduruu Puteoli.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ɛhɔ na yɛhunuu anuanom bie, na wɔsrɛɛ yɛn sɛ yɛntena wɔn nkyɛn nnanson. Na yɛfiri hɔ kɔduruu Roma.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ɛhɔ na anuanom a wɔtee yɛn nka no firi bɛhyiaa yɛn Apia dwa mu ne akuraa bi a ɛde Nsadan-Mmiɛnsa, na Paulo hunuu wɔn no, ɔdaa Onyankopɔn ase, na ɔmaa ne bo tɔɔ ne yam.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na yɛduruu Roma no, wɔmaa Paulo kwan sɛ ɔne ɔsraani a ɔhwɛ no no nkɔtena faako a ɔpɛ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ nnansa akyiri no, Paulo frɛfrɛɛ Yudafoɔ atitire no hyiae; na wɔbaeɛ no, ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Anuanom, manyɛ biribi mantia ɔman anaa yɛn agyanom amanneɛ deɛ, nanso wɔkyeree me Yerusalem de me hyɛɛ Romafoɔ nsa.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na wɔn nso, wɔhwehwɛɛ asɛm no mu no, wɔpɛɛ sɛ anka wɔgyaa me, ɛfiri sɛ menyɛɛ adeɛ biara a ɛfata okum.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Nanso Yudafoɔ kasa tiaeɛ nti, na ɛtwa sɛ mede m’asɛm mekɔdan Kaesare; na ɛnyɛ sɛ me ne me man wɔ nkuro bi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Afei yei nti na mefrɛɛ mo, sɛ mɛhu mo, na makasa makyerɛ mo; ɛfiri sɛ Israel anidasoɔ nti na wɔde nkɔnsɔnkɔnsɔn yi agu me yi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na wɔka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Yɛn deɛ, yɛnnyaa wo ho nwoma bi mfirii Yudea, nanso anuanom no mu biara mma mmɛbɔɔ kaseɛ, anaasɛ ɔmmɛkaa wo ho asɛmmɔne bi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na yɛpɛ sɛ yɛtie deɛ wo ara wodwene, na fekuo yi deɛ, yɛnim sɛ wɔkasa tia wɔ mmaa nyinaa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wɔhyɛɛ no da no, nnipa bebree baa ne nkyɛn faako a ɔteɛ hɔ; na ɔkyerɛɛ wɔn aseɛ dii Nyankopɔn ahennie ho adanseɛ, na ɔde Mose mmara ne adiyifoɔ no kyerɛɛ wɔn Yesu ho nsɛm no firi anɔpa kɔsii anwummerɛ.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ebinom gyee deɛ ɔkaeɛ no dii, na ebinom nso annye anni.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na wɔn ano ankɔ bɛnkorɔ mu nti, wɔkɔe, berɛ a Paulo kaa asɛm baako sɛ: Nokwasɛm na Honhom Kronkron nam Odiyifoɔ Yesaia so ka kyerɛɛ mo agyanom sɛ:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Kɔ ɔman yi nkyɛn, na kɔka sɛ: Ɛteɛ deɛ, mobɛte, na morente aseɛ, na ehunu nso, mobɛhunu, na morenhunu mu.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na ɔman yi akoma apirim, na wɔmfa wɔn aso nte asɛm yie, na wɔamuamua wɔn ani; na wɔamfa wɔn ani anhunu adeɛ, na wɔamfa wɔn aso ante asɛm, na wɔamfa wɔn akoma ante aseɛ, na wɔannane amma me nkyɛn na mansa wɔn yadeɛ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Enti monhunu sɛ wɔama wɔde Nyankopɔn nkwagyeɛ no akɔma amanaman mufoɔ; na wɔbɛte.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> [Na ɔkaa nsɛm yi no, Yudafoɔ no kɔe, na wɔgyegye akyinnyeɛ pii wɔn mu.]",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na mfeɛ mmienu kusuu na ɔde tenaa ɔno ara ne fie a ɔtua ka no mu, na ɔgyee wɔn a wɔbaa ne nkyɛn nyinaa",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> kaa Nyankopɔn ahennie ho asɛm, na ɔde nnam nyinaa kyerɛkyerɛɛ nnoɔma a ɛfa Awurade Yesu Kristo ho, na obiara ansi no kwan."
		}
	}
};
